 Best Amazon Affiliate WordPress Plugins (Compared)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-amazon-affiliate-wordpress-plugins/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-amazon-affiliate-wordpress-plugins/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 04 Aug 2020 09:00:12 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"WordPress Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:24:\"amazon affiliate plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34:\"amazon affiliate wordpress plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"best amazon affiliate plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"best amazon affiliate wordpress plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34:\"wordpress amazon affiliate plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=247503\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:615:\"<p>Are you looking for the best Amazon affiliate WordPress plugin? Amazon offers one of the best affiliate programs in the world. You can integrate Amazon products on your website or blog to earn money from affiliate partners. Amazon affiliate plugins let you display products on your site and keep them up to date for features, [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-amazon-affiliate-wordpress-plugins/\">9 Best Amazon Affiliate WordPress Plugins (Compared)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - Free WordPress Theme Detector</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13762:\"<p>Are you looking for the best Amazon affiliate WordPress plugin?</p>\n<p>Amazon offers one of the best affiliate programs in the world. You can integrate Amazon products on your website or blog to earn money from affiliate partners.</p>\n<p>Amazon affiliate plugins let you display products on your site and keep them up to date for features, prices, and other details. This way, you can spend less time on the setup and more time on the growth of your business.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share some of the best Amazon affiliate WordPress plugins that you can use.</p>\n<h3>Best Amazon Affiliate WordPress Plugins</h3>\n<p>Below you will find our handpicked list of the best Amazon affiliate WordPress plugins. It includes paid and free plugins, so you can select the right affiliate plugin for your website.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/pretty-links-pro/\" title=\"Pretty Links Pro\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">1. Pretty Links Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/pretty-links-pro/\" title=\"Pretty Links Pro\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/prettylinks.png\" alt=\"PrettyLinks Pro\" width=\"775\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247552\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/prettylinks.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/prettylinks-300x116.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/prettylinks-768x297.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/pretty-links-pro/\" title=\"Pretty Links Pro\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Pretty Links Pro</a> is the beginner-friendly WordPress affiliate marketing plugin. It maximizes your affiliate income from the existing content on your website by letting you create, manage, and cloak affiliate links on your site. </p>\n<p>If you integrate Amazon products on your website or blog, Pretty Links Pro can help add affiliate links automatically. Not only does it create links, but you can also share the affiliate links in your emails, podcasts, YouTube videos, and so on.</p>\n<p>It comes with a URL shortener to make custom shareable links for your products. That way, you can promote Amazon products more efficiently and increase your revenue.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> $49 &#8211; $149</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/aawp/\" title=\"AAWP\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">2. AAWP</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/aawp/\" title=\"AAWP\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/aawp.png\" alt=\"AAWP\" width=\"775\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247551\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/aawp.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/aawp-300x116.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/aawp-768x297.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/aawp/\" title=\"AAWP\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">AAWP</a> is one of the best WordPress Amazon affiliate plugins on the planet. It automatically generates affiliate links, updates products and prices, and displays new discounts.</p>\n<p>You can use this plugin to promote Amazon products and make a living from your website. It&#8217;s highly flexible for general settings and individual product options.</p>\n<p>The plugin lets you choose between different design options to display products. You can also add custom styles or make new templates that best match your theme.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> $46 &#8211; $348</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/thirstyaffiliates/\" title=\"ThirstyAffiliates\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">3. ThirstyAffiliates</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/thirstyaffiliates/\" title=\"ThirstyAffiliates\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/thirsty-affiliates.png\" alt=\"ThirstyAffiliates\" width=\"775\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247553\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/thirsty-affiliates.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/thirsty-affiliates-300x116.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/thirsty-affiliates-768x297.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/thirstyaffiliates/\" title=\"ThirstyAffiliates\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">ThirstyAffiliate</a> is a popular WordPress affiliate link cloaking plugin. It lets you easily add Amazon affiliate links to your pages and posts.</p>\n<p>It comes with an auto-link feature to automatically link to your provided keywords. With the import option, you can import/export affiliate links between your sites in just a few clicks.</p>\n<p>The plugin offers useful reports and statistics to the website admin. You can analyze these reports to add better and more user-friendly affiliate links to your website.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> $49 &#8211; $149</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/code-canyon-wzone-woocommerce/\" title=\"WZone\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">4. WZone</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/code-canyon-wzone-woocommerce/\" title=\"WZone\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/wzone.png\" alt=\"WZone\" width=\"775\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247554\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/wzone.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/wzone-300x116.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/wzone-768x297.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/code-canyon-wzone-woocommerce/\" title=\"WZone\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">WZone</a> is a WordPress WooCommerce Amazon affiliates plugin. It comes with multiple product import options based on your preferences and keywords.</p>\n<p>The best part about the plugin is that you can set up product pages quickly with autopilot mode. It lets you manage, publish, and delete the products within the dashboard.</p>\n<p>Other notable features include Amazon recommendations that you can use to display top products matching your business or niche. It also shares reports and stats, so you&#8217;ll know about the most popular products on your website.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> $49</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/amalinks-pro/\" title=\"AmaLinks Pro\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">5. AmaLinks Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/amalinks-pro/\" title=\"AmaLinks Pro\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/amalinks-pro.png\" alt=\"AmaLinks Pro\" width=\"775\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247546\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/amalinks-pro.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/amalinks-pro-300x116.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/amalinks-pro-768x297.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/amalinks-pro/\" title=\"AmaLinks Pro\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">AmaLinks Pro</a> is an excellent WordPress Amazon affiliate plugin. It lets you create, preview, edit, and insert Amazon affiliate links in your posts with just a few clicks.</p>\n<p>You can add Amazon&#8217;s call to action buttons to maximize the click-through rates on your website. The plugin lets you showcase product information, images, ratings, reviews, and links directly from Amazon.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> $67 &#8211; $597 </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/amazon-auto-links/\" title=\"Amazon Auto Links\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">6. Amazon Auto Links</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/amazon-auto-links/\" title=\"Amazon Auto Links\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/amazon-auto-links.png\" alt=\"Amazon Auto Links\" width=\"775\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247547\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/amazon-auto-links.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/amazon-auto-links-300x116.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/amazon-auto-links-768x297.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/amazon-auto-links/\" title=\"Amazon Auto Links\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Amazon Auto Links</a> is a free WordPress Amazon affiliate plugin. It comes with simple settings to display Amazon products on your website and keep them up-to-date.</p>\n<p>You can select specific categories, and the plugin will showcase products automatically. The products will have affiliate links, so you can generate income with less effort.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> FREE</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/amazon-product-in-a-post-plugin/\" title=\"Amazon Product in a Post\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">7. Amazon Product in a Post</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/amazon-product-in-a-post-plugin/\" title=\"Amazon Product in a Post\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/amazon-product-in-post.jpg\" alt=\"Amazon Product in a Post\" width=\"775\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247548\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/amazon-product-in-post.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/amazon-product-in-post-300x116.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/amazon-product-in-post-768x297.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/amazon-product-in-a-post-plugin/\" title=\"Amazon Product in a Post\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Amazon Product in a Post</a> is a WordPress Amazon affiliate plugin to add products and items on your pages/posts. It uses the Amazon product identification number and API key for integration.</p>\n<p>You need to create an Amazon affiliate account and get the free Amazon API key to start adding products on your website. The plugin lets you display products at the top, bottom, or middle of the content.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> Free</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/affiliatewp/\" title=\"AffiliateWP\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">8. AffiliateWP</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/affiliatewp/\" title=\"AffiliateWP\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/affiliatewp.png\" alt=\"AffiliateWP\" width=\"775\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247549\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/affiliatewp.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/affiliatewp-300x116.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/affiliatewp-768x297.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/affiliatewp/\" title=\"AffiliateWP\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">AffiliateWP</a> is a premium WordPress affiliate marketing solution. It&#8217;s easy to use, reliable, and provides affiliate marketing tools to grow your business.</p>\n<p>You can use this plugin to add Amazon affiliate links on your website and make money online. It tracks affiliate referrals and shows real-time reports to take quick actions to improve your website.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> $99 &#8211; $499</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/easyazon/\" title=\"EasyAzon\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">9. EasyAzon</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/easyazon/\" title=\"EasyAzon\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/easyazon.jpg\" alt=\"EasyAzon\" width=\"775\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247550\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/easyazon.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/easyazon-300x116.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/easyazon-768x297.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/easyazon/\" title=\"EasyAzon\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">EasyAzon</a> is another free Amazon affiliate WordPress plugin. It lets you create affiliate links within your WordPress post editor for any Amazon product.</p>\n<p>It supports all locations that offer an Amazon Associates affiliate program. The plugin settings are easy to manage and configure without editing any code.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> Free</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you find the best Amazon affiliate WordPress plugin for your site.</p>\n<p>You may also want to check out our complete guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-amazon-affiliate-store-wordpress-make-money/\" title=\"How to Create an Amazon Affiliate Store (Step by Step)\">how to create an Amazon affiliate store</a> to make money online.</p>\n<p>This will help take your affiliate marketing strategy to the next level! </p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-amazon-affiliate-wordpress-plugins/\">9 Best Amazon Affiliate WordPress Plugins (Compared)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - Free WordPress Theme Detector</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-amazon-affiliate-wordpress-plugins/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:49:\"10 Best Timeline Plugins for WordPress (Compared)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"https://www.isitwp.com/timeline-plugins-for-wordpress/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"https://www.isitwp.com/timeline-plugins-for-wordpress/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 03 Aug 2020 09:00:13 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"WordPress Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"best timeline plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:35:\"best timeline plugins for WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"best wordpress timeline plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=247371\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:564:\"<p>Do you want to use a timeline or roadmap on your website to show the growth of your business? You may want to consider using a timeline plugin. Timeline plugins can help narrate your story in a visual way that is engaging and easy to understand for your audience. You can use it to show [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/timeline-plugins-for-wordpress/\">10 Best Timeline Plugins for WordPress (Compared)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - Free WordPress Theme Detector</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17559:\"<p>Do you want to use a timeline or roadmap on your website to show the growth of your business? </p>\n<p>You may want to consider using a timeline plugin. Timeline plugins can help narrate your story in a visual way that is engaging and easy to understand for your audience. </p>\n<p>You can use it to show your struggles, achievements, and milestones in a chronological way in the form of a timeline. Many big brands choose to showcase their business story in this way. This helps them show their credibility and build trust among their audience. </p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll tell you about the best timeline plugins that can help you create a timeline without any coding skills needed. But before that, let&#8217;s check out some of the features you should look for in a timeline plugin. </p>\n<h3>What Features to Look for in a Timeline Plugin</h3>\n<p>The best way to select a timeline plugin is to check their demos. This can help you find out which features are offered by the plugin. Depending on the purpose of creating your timeline, the feature requirements may vary for every user. </p>\n<p>However, having the following features on your plugin can be really helpful for you to create beautiful and engaging timelines for your website:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Support for media and text files</li>\n<li>Social sharing options</li>\n<li>Pre-built templates for an easy start</li>\n</ul>\n<p>All of these elements can make your timeline share a more engaging story with your audience. </p>\n<p>Having said that, let&#8217;s now look at some of the plugins that you can try out. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/accesspress-everest-timeline/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >1. Everest Timeline</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/accesspress-everest-timeline/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Everest_Timeline.png\" alt=\"timeline plugins\" width=\"775\" height=\"392\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-247381\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Everest_Timeline.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Everest_Timeline-300x152.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Everest_Timeline-768x388.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/accesspress-everest-timeline/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Everest Timeline</a> is a responsive timeline plugin that can help you create a beautiful timeline for your website. It offers 50+ pre-built templates to help you get started easily. It offers various layout options like vertical, horizontal, one-side layout, Facebook layouts, and more to make your timeline look unique. </p>\n<p>It also supports different media files like images, videos from different sources like YouTube and Vimeo, and more. To make your timeline stand out, you can use its stunning filters. Apart from that, you also have the option to add social share buttons to your timeline. </p>\n<p>Everest Timeline offers everything you need to create a perfect timeline for your business. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/timeline-express/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">2. Timeline Express</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/timeline-express/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Timeline_Express.png\" alt=\"Timeline_Express\" width=\"775\" height=\"243\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-247396\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Timeline_Express.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Timeline_Express-300x94.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Timeline_Express-768x241.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/timeline-express/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Timeline Express</a> is a free timeline plugin that offers great features to create animated vertical timelines for your business. The plugin offers a shortcode for any timeline you create. You can paste these shortcodes within your posts and pages wherever you want to display them. </p>\n<p>The plugin lets you use various fonts, icons, and images on your timeline to make it look more interesting. The plugin is cross-browser compatible and looks stunning across devices. It also has a <a href=\"https://www.wp-timelineexpress.com/pricing/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">pro version</a> available with even more features.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/plugins/essential-addons-elementor/#pricing\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">3. Essential Addons</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/plugins/essential-addons-elementor/#pricing\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Essential-Addons.png\" alt=\"Essential Addons\" width=\"775\" height=\"309\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-247388\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Essential-Addons.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Essential-Addons-300x120.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Essential-Addons-768x306.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/plugins/essential-addons-elementor/#pricing\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Essential Addons</a> isn&#8217;t a plugin but a powerful addon that can help you create timelines for your website. You can use this addon only if you&#8217;re using the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/elementor-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Elementor</a> page builder to create your website designs. </p>\n<p>You can learn <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/elementor/\">more about Elementor here</a>.</p>\n<p>By installing this addon, you not only get to create timelines but can also extend your features to create accordions, pricing tables, filterable galleries, countdown timers, and a lot more. It lets you display blog posts, pages, or custom posts in a stunning vertical layout. You can set your preferred number of posts, add amazing effects, image overlay, buttons, and more in your timelines with this addon. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://cooltimeline.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">4. Cool Timeline</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://cooltimeline.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Cool_Timeline_Pro_WordPress_Best_Timeline_Plugin_10000_Installs.png\" alt=\"cool timeline\" width=\"775\" height=\"325\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-247397\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Cool_Timeline_Pro_WordPress_Best_Timeline_Plugin_10000_Installs.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Cool_Timeline_Pro_WordPress_Best_Timeline_Plugin_10000_Installs-300x126.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Cool_Timeline_Pro_WordPress_Best_Timeline_Plugin_10000_Installs-768x322.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://cooltimeline.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Cool Timeline</a> is another amazing timeline plugin that can help you tell your story in the form of a timeline. It offers 20+ horizontal and vertical timeline styles to make it look unique and interesting. You can also use it to convert your blogs to a cool timeline. </p>\n<p>The plugin offers extensive customization options and supports various multimedia files like videos, images, sliders, and more. The plugin is compatible with different page builders like Elementor, WPBakery, and other popular choices. </p>\n<p>Cool Timeline is user-friendly and has extensive documentation to help you troubleshoot and solve your problems. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.wp-timelineexpress.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">5. Timeline Express</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wp-timelineexpress.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Timeline_Express-1.png\" alt=\"Timeline_Express, timeline plugins\" width=\"775\" height=\"336\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-247399\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Timeline_Express-1.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Timeline_Express-1-300x130.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Timeline_Express-1-768x333.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wp-timelineexpress.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Timeline Express</a> makes it easy for you to create beautiful timelines for your WordPress website. It lets you offer an animated vertical layout that will quickly engage your users with your story. You can also add hundreds of icons, video banners, and different animated styles to make your timeline more interactive. </p>\n<p>The plugin is super easy to set up and use. It also has a 15-day money-back guarantee. So if you don&#8217;t like its features after purchasing it, you can get your money back within 15 days of your purchase. Timeline Express supports different languages, advanced timeline styles, and a lot more. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/rich-event-timeline/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">6. Event Timeline</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/rich-event-timeline/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Event-Timeline.png\" alt=\"Event Timeline\" width=\"775\" height=\"238\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-247400\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Event-Timeline.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Event-Timeline-300x92.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Event-Timeline-768x236.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/rich-event-timeline/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Event Timeline</a> is a free timeline plugin that lets you create vertical and horizontal timelines that look amazing across all devices. To help you get started quickly, it offers 18 beautiful themes, each of which is super flexible. </p>\n<p>It also supports 2 different styles: classic and modern. You can select the one that you think looks best on your website. The plugin also supports various media files including videos. The color picker makes it easy to choose your own color. Because of the clean code used to design the plugin, it looks stunning across all devices. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/timeline-and-history-slider/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">7. Timeline and History Slider</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/timeline-and-history-slider/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Timeline_and_History_slider.png\" alt=\"Timeline_and_History_slider\" width=\"775\" height=\"218\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-247401\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Timeline_and_History_slider.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Timeline_and_History_slider-300x84.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Timeline_and_History_slider-768x216.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/timeline-and-history-slider/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Timeline and History</a> is a free timeline plugin that lets you add your business history or timeline to your WordPress website without writing any code. You can also add a title and featured image to make it easy for users to understand your timeline better. </p>\n<p>Timeline and History Slider lets you create a timeline of your blog posts in a horizontal order based on the year and date of your posts. The plugin is super easy to use and works alongside all modern plugins and themes. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/post-timeline/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">8. Post Timeline</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/post-timeline/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Post_Timeline.png\" alt=\"timeline plugins\" width=\"775\" height=\"241\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-247402\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Post_Timeline.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Post_Timeline-300x93.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Post_Timeline-768x239.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/post-timeline/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Post Timeline</a> is the next plugin that you should check out. It&#8217;s a powerful and user-friendly plugin that offers you quick and easy ways to add vertical timelines to your website. It will also automatically create animated scroll navigation based on Tag or dates in ascending order. </p>\n<p>With this plugin, you can create as many timelines as you want for free. It also offers the flexibility to assign icons and set different colors to your timeline. This makes it more appealing for your users to look at. To help you reach out to a larger audience, Post Timeline supports multiple languages. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/timeline-for-beaver-builder/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">9. Timeline Module for Beaver Builder</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/timeline-for-beaver-builder/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Timeline_Module_for_Beaver_Builder.png\" alt=\"Timeline_Module_for_Beaver_Builder, timeline plugin, timeline plugins\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-247404\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Timeline_Module_for_Beaver_Builder.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Timeline_Module_for_Beaver_Builder-300x132.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Timeline_Module_for_Beaver_Builder-768x337.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/timeline-for-beaver-builder/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Timeline Module for Beaver Builder</a> is a free plugin that adds the module for adding a timeline to your Beaver Builder plugin. With this plugin, you can easily display your company history and its progress or list your personal achievements in the form of a timeline. </p>\n<p>The plugin offers various typography options for your titles, descriptions, dates, or any other content that you add. You can also hide or show your timeline date, enable or disable the connectors, and do a lot more.   </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/code-canyon-content-timeline-plugin/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >10. Content Timeline</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/code-canyon-content-timeline-plugin/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Content_Timeline_Responsive_WordPress_Plugin-1.png\" alt=\"Content_Timeline_Responsive_WordPress_Plugin, timeline plugin, timeline plugins\" width=\"775\" height=\"388\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-247406\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Content_Timeline_Responsive_WordPress_Plugin-1.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Content_Timeline_Responsive_WordPress_Plugin-1-300x150.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Content_Timeline_Responsive_WordPress_Plugin-1-768x384.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/code-canyon-content-timeline-plugin/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Content Timeline</a> is another powerful, lightweight and responsive timeline plugin that offers an easy way to organize your content in the form of a timeline. You can use 12 different card layouts that can quickly enhance the look of your timeline. </p>\n<p>Creating these timelines with Content Timeline is super quick and easy. Just take any content, sort it by date, add call functions, and you&#8217;re good to go. With the 50 different settings that it offers for customization, you can make your timeline appear even more stunning.</p>\n<p>These are some of the best timeline plugins that you can check out. We hope you found this article helpful. </p>\n<p>And since you&#8217;re looking for a timeline plugin, we thought you might also be interested in learning <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/make-an-online-portfolio/\">how to create an online portfolio</a>. </p>\n<p>Creating your portfolio can be a good idea if you want to showcase your personal achievements for potential customers or clients. Plus, it pairs well with the plugins listed in this post because you can show those achievements in the form of a timeline on your portfolio.  </p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/timeline-plugins-for-wordpress/\">10 Best Timeline Plugins for WordPress (Compared)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - Free WordPress Theme Detector</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"https://www.isitwp.com/timeline-plugins-for-wordpress/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"15+ Best Cleaning Services WordPress Themes in 2020\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_b