{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:614:\"<p>Are you looking for the best cleaning services WordPress themes? If you run a cleaning service website, you&#8217;ll need to make sure the theme you choose is a perfect fit for your business. In this article, we will share some of the best cleaning services WordPress themes that you can use. Best Cleaning Services WordPress [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-cleaning-services-wordpress-themes/\">15+ Best Cleaning Services WordPress Themes in 2020</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - Free WordPress Theme Detector</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26553:\"<p>Are you looking for the best cleaning services WordPress themes?</p>\n<p>If you run a cleaning service website, you&#8217;ll need to make sure the theme you choose is a perfect fit for your business. </p>\n<p>In this article, we will share some of the best cleaning services WordPress themes that you can use.</p>\n<h3>Best Cleaning Services WordPress Themes</h3>\n<p>Below you will find our handpicked list of the best cleaning services WordPress themes. It includes free and paid themes, so you can select a cleaning services theme that suits best for your website.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/astra-wordpress-theme/\" title=\"Astra Theme\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">1. Astra</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/astra-wordpress-theme/\" title=\"Astra Theme\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/astra-3.jpg\" alt=\"Astra\" width=\"775\" height=\"440\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247332\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/astra-3.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/astra-3-300x170.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/astra-3-768x436.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/astra-wordpress-theme/\" title=\"Astra Theme\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Astra</a> is a highly flexible WordPress theme built for any type of website. It comes with dozens of starter sites and a free importer plugin to help you launch your cleaning services website quickly.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fast and lightweight</li>\n<li>Supports <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-page-builders-compared/\" title=\"7 Best Drag and Drop WordPress Page Builders\">page builders</a></li>\n<li>Color schemes</li>\n<li>Custom background</li>\n<li>Call-to-action buttons</li>\n<li>And more&#8230;</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/astra-wordpress-theme/\" title=\"Astra Theme\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Get the Astra theme today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/divi/\" title=\"Divi\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">2. Divi</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/divi/\" title=\"Divi\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/divi-3.jpg\" alt=\"Divi\" width=\"775\" height=\"440\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247333\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/divi-3.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/divi-3-300x170.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/divi-3-768x436.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/divi/\" title=\"Divi\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Divi</a> is one of the most popular WordPress multipurpose themes. It lets you create a cleaning services and maintenance website without writing a single line of code.</p>\n<p>Divi comes in 2 products: Divi Theme and Divi Builder plugin. </p>\n<p>Divi Theme is best for users who want to make customization by using one of its 100+ full site packs that come along with the theme. </p>\n<p>The Divi Builder plugin works with any theme, is best for users who want to use it alongside other themes.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Image filters</li>\n<li>Text styles</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-ecommerce-plugins-compared/\" title=\"6 BEST WordPress eCommerce Plugins\">eCommerce</a> integration</li>\n<li>Custom widgets</li>\n<li>Translation ready</li>\n<li>And more&#8230;</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/divi/\" title=\"Divi\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Get the Divi theme today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/oceanwp/\" title=\"OceanWP\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">3. OceanWP</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/oceanwp/\" title=\"OceanWP\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/oceanwp-3.jpg\" alt=\"OceanWP\" width=\"775\" height=\"440\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247334\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/oceanwp-3.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/oceanwp-3-300x170.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/oceanwp-3-768x436.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/oceanwp/\" title=\"OceanWP\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">OceanWP</a> is a free WordPress all-purpose theme with premium-like features and custom layouts. It comes with multiple cleaning services templates that you can import in 1-click to set up your website.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Social media widgets</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-woocommerce-plugins-grow-sales-rapidly/\" title=\"29 Best WooCommerce Plugins to Grow Sales Rapidly\">WooCommerce</a> compatibility</li>\n<li>Fullscreen layouts</li>\n<li>Notification bars</li>\n<li>Built-in extensions</li>\n<li>And more&#8230;</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/oceanwp/\" title=\"OceanWP\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Get the OceanWP theme today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-corporate-pro/\" title=\"Corporate\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">4. Corporate Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-corporate-pro/\" title=\"Corporate\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/corporate-pro.jpg\" alt=\"Corporate Pro\" width=\"775\" height=\"440\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247335\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/corporate-pro.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/corporate-pro-300x170.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/corporate-pro-768x436.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-corporate-pro/\" title=\"Corporate\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Corporate Pro</a> is a modern WordPress theme built on top of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-genesis/\" title=\"Genesis Framework\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Genesis Framework</a>. It offer a professional and elegant design that engages your users on the website.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>1-click demo importer</li>\n<li>Widgetized homepage</li>\n<li>Custom header</li>\n<li>Landing pages</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-social-media-plugins/\" title=\"12 Best WordPress Social Media Plugins for Engagement\">Social media icons</a></li>\n<li>And more&#8230;</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-corporate-pro/\" title=\"Corporate\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Get the Corporate Pro theme today!</a></p>\n<div class=\"alert alert-success\"><strong><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpengine/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >FREE ACCESS: Corporate Pro + 35 Other StudioPress Themes!</a></strong> </p>\n<p>Want to try all the premium StudioPress themes, including Corporate Pro, for FREE?</p>\n<p>When you sign up for <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpengine/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >WP Engine</a>, the best managed WordPress hosting service, you receive the Genesis framework and ALL StudioPress themes for free (That&#8217;s over $2,000 in value!)</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpengine/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Get All 35+ Themes for FREE With WP Engine</a></div>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/inkthemes-servingmaid/\" title=\"Maid Services\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">5. Maid Services</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/inkthemes-servingmaid/\" title=\"Maid Services\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/maid-services.jpg\" alt=\"Maid Services\" width=\"775\" height=\"440\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247336\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/maid-services.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/maid-services-300x170.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/maid-services-768x436.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/inkthemes-servingmaid/\" title=\"Maid Services\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Maid Services</a> is a classic WordPress cleaning service theme built specifically for serving maids, housekeeping agencies, domestic help providers, and other related companies. It helps promote your services to the right audiences and get new customers from the website.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Boxed slider</li>\n<li>Welcome note</li>\n<li>3-column layout</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpml/\" title=\"WPML\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">WPML</a> integration</li>\n<li>Blog page template</li>\n<li>And more&#8230;</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/inkthemes-servingmaid/\" title=\"Maid Services\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Get the Maid Services theme today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/theme-forest-clenix/\" title=\"Clenix\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">6. Clenix</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/theme-forest-clenix/\" title=\"Clenix\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/clenix.jpg\" alt=\"Clenix\" width=\"775\" height=\"440\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247337\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/clenix.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/clenix-300x170.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/clenix-768x436.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/theme-forest-clenix/\" title=\"Clenix\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Clenix</a> is a professional WordPress cleaning services theme. It has a modern design with 4 multi-page demos, custom page layouts, and homepage sections.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/elementor-pro/\" title=\"Elementor Pro\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank