";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15968:\"<p>Are you looking for a directory plugin for your website?</p>\n<p>By using a directory plugin, you can list different businesses from various niches in your community to build a local directory. This can be a real estate site listing, a yellow page style business directory, a restaurant business listing, medical practitioners listing, or anything in your niche. </p>\n<p>A perfect example is a review site like Yelp. </p>\n<p>Visitors can use your directory to find things like contact details, images, location, and other information about the businesses that are listed on it. You can also allow people to list their own businesses for more exposure. </p>\n<p>Users can create an account and add images, locations, and contact details of their businesses for visitors to find them easily. In return, you can charge a small amount for hosting their business on your directory site. </p>\n<p>Doing this is a great way of <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/legit-ways-to-make-money-online-blogging/\">making money online</a>. </p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll tell you about some of the popular directory plugins that can help you create a directory site without the help of a professional. But before that, let&#8217;s find out what features to look for in a good directory plugin. </p>\n<h3>What Features to Look for in a Directory Plugin</h3>\n<p>The features you want on your directory plugin can vary based on the type of directory you&#8217;re creating. But most good directory plugins will have the following features in common. </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Rating and review options</li>\n<li>Features for adding new listings</li>\n<li>Location-based search module with maps</li>\n<li>Front-end submission support</li>\n<li>Multi-media file support</li>\n<li>Payment support</li>\n</ul>\n<p>All of these features make a more user-friendly directory site that&#8217;s easy to manage. Now, let&#8217;s check out the best directory plugins available on the market.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/formidable-forms/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >1. Formidable Forms</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/formidable-forms/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/formidable-forms-review.png\" alt=\"formidable forms, directory plugins, restaurant menu plugins\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-223636\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/formidable-forms-review.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/formidable-forms-review-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/formidable-forms-review-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/formidable-forms/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Formidable Forms</a> is a great option for a directory plugin. With this plugin, <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/plugins/how-to-create-a-web-directory-in-wordpress/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">creating a directory</a> is easy. You can create a form and add the calculating fields manually or import it from a CSV file if you already have the data saved. </p>\n<p>These forms also have the front-end editing feature so that new users can quickly edit or add information without logging into your site. Apart from that, it offers the search option for visitors to search for a specific business by name, age, or location. </p>\n<p>When the users find the business they&#8217;re looking for, they can use the contact form on your website to get in touch with you. With many other powerful features, it is a great directory plugin to use on your site. Check out this review to learn <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/formidable-forms/\">more about Formidable Forms</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wp-geo-directory/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >2. WP GeoDirectory</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wp-geo-directory/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WPGEO-1.jpg\" alt=\"WP Geo Directory\" width=\"775\" height=\"263\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247278\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WPGEO-1.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WPGEO-1-300x102.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WPGEO-1-768x261.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wp-geo-directory/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >WP GeoDirectory</a> is another amazing directory plugin that lets you list millions of businesses on your website. The plugin has been designed with clean code that can handle high to very high traffic without any performance issues.</p>\n<p>Visitors can use the drag and drop builder to make front-end submissions. The plugin is super flexible and lets you customize every bit of it without any coding needed. You can also add widgets for maps to your listings so that visitors can easily find them. </p>\n<p>All in all, WP Geo Directory is a good solution if you want to build a directory site.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://businessdirectoryplugin.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">3. Business Directory Plugin</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://businessdirectoryplugin.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Business_Directory_Plugin.png\" alt=\"Business_Directory_Plugin\" width=\"775\" height=\"270\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247281\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Business_Directory_Plugin.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Business_Directory_Plugin-300x105.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Business_Directory_Plugin-768x268.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://businessdirectoryplugin.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Business Directory </a> is a powerful directory plugin that lets you create any kind of directory for your site. The plugin lets you add an unlimited number of listings that can also be imported by CSV. To make it easy for you to get started, it offers various pre-built templates, too. These templates can be customized with a few clicks.</p>\n<p>To let you monetize your site, Business Directory supports various payment gateways like PayPal, Stripe, and more. To let you expand your reach, it also lets you translate your site to various languages. </p>\n<p>Business Directory is a solid option if you take payments or want an international directory site.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/code-canyon-sabai-directory/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >4. Sabai Directory</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/code-canyon-sabai-directory/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Sabai_Directory.png\" alt=\"Sabai_Directory plugin\" width=\"775\" height=\"376\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247285\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Sabai_Directory.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Sabai_Directory-300x146.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Sabai_Directory-768x373.png 768w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Sabai_Directory-330x160.png 330w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/code-canyon-sabai-directory/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Sabai Directory</a> is a powerful premium directory plugin that lets you build community-driven local business directories like Yelp. With this plugin, you can display your listings in the form of lists, grids, or map view format. The listing can be filtered and reviewed by custom fields. </p>\n<p>You can add pictures to your listings to make it more useful for your users. Visitors can upvote the image you add and comment on them as well. It also has multi-location support. You can have a featured listing, paid listing option with custom price plans, accept payments on your site, and do a lot more with Sabai Directory. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/connections/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">5. Connections</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/connections/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Connections.png\" alt=\"Connections\" width=\"775\" height=\"258\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247283\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Connections.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Connections-300x100.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Connections-768x256.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/connections/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Conections</a> is a free yet powerful directory plugin that you can try out. You can use it with some of the most popular themes like Divi, Avada, OceanWP, and others. It&#8217;s easy to design your directory because the plugin is compatible with page builders like Elementor, Beaver Builder, Brizy, Visual Composer, and so on.</p>\n<p>You can also add your own logo, pictures of staff from each of the listed businesses, and a lot more. The plugin also supports easy CSV import/export of your entries. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/advanced-classifieds-and-directory-pro/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">6. Advanced Classifieds and Directory Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/advanced-classifieds-and-directory-pro/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Advanced-classified.png\" alt=\"Advanced classified\" width=\"775\" height=\"250\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247284\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Advanced-classified.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Advanced-classified-300x97.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Advanced-classified-768x248.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/advanced-classifieds-and-directory-pro/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Advanced Classifieds and Directory Pro</a> is a flexible and high-quality WordPress plugin that can let you create a very professional directory for your website. It lets you add an unlimited number of categories and category levels to your listings. It also supports adaptable field type formats like radio, checkbox, select list, and more. </p>\n<p>You can also easily integrate <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/google-maps-builder/\">Google maps</a> with your listings so that visitors are able to easily locate them. As the admin of your website, you can have full control over your listings in the backend. This includes adding new listings, categories, locations, editing their details, and more. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/business-directory-plugin/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">7. Business Directory Plugin</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/business-directory-plugin/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Business_Directory_Plugin-1.png\" alt=\"Business_Directory_Plugin\" width=\"775\" height=\"250\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247282\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Business_Directory_Plugin-1.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Business_Directory_Plugin-1-300x97.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Business_Directory_Plugin-1-768x248.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /> </a></p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/business-directory-plugin/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Business Directory</a> plugin is a free directory plugin that makes it easy to create a local directory or start a provider list for your visitors. The plugin also lets you upload images and PDF files to your listings. You can display the location of your listing and make locating them quick and simple. </p>\n<p>To make it easy for you to accept payments, this plugin supports different payment gateways like PayPal, Stripe, and more. The plugin integrates with various popular plugins, so it&#8217;s really easy to expand your website features. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/name-directory/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">8. BePro Listing</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/bepro-listings/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/BePro_Listings.png\" alt=\"BePro_Listings, directory plugins\" width=\"775\" height=\"248\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247286\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/BePro_Listings.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/BePro_Listings-300x96.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/BePro_Listings-768x246.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>With <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/bepro-listings/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">BePro Listing</a> creating directories is super easy. It lets your visitors submit their business listing along with their prices, images, contact details, and other information with the help of the front-end submission feature. </p>\n<p>The plugin is super flexible, and you can set it up within minutes.   </p>\n<p>It also lets your visitors search and filter through listings in various ways, including optional Google maps and several search result layouts. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/name-directory/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">9. Name Directory</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/name-directory/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Name_Directory.png\" alt=\"Name_Directory\" width=\"775\" height=\"241\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247287\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Name_Directory.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Name_Directory-300x93.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Name_Directory-768x239.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/name-directory/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Name Directory</a> is a free yet powerful directory plugin which lets you create directories in the form of a glossary/index. It supports multiple directories in a single installation, and you can show/hide your title, description, suggestion form, and other information as well. You can also enable the search feature for your directories for a better user experience. </p>\n<p>And there you have it! These are some of the best directory plugins that can help you create beautiful local directories without writing any code. We hope you found this article helpful. </p>\n<p>When you&#8217;re done creating your directory, you might want more people to find your website. The best way to do that is to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/complete-wordpress-seo-guide-beginners/\">work on your SEO</a>. </p>\n<p>This will help you get your website on the top of the search results for Google, which will help you get more traffic. </p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-directory-plugins/\">9 Best WordPress Directory Plugins for 2020 (Compared)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - Free WordPress Theme Detector</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-directory-plugins/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"12 Best Forum Plugins for WordPress Compared &amp; Reviewed\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-forum-plugin-for-wordpress/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-forum-plugin-for-wordpress/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 29 Jul 2020 17:49:57 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"WordPress Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"best wordpress forum plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"forum plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26:\"foum plugins for wordpress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=247506\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:660:\"<p>Do you want to create a forum for your WordPress website? Forums are online communities where like-minded people can communicate through conversational threads. It&#8217;s a wonderful platform to engage your audience in a two-way dialogue. Plus, community members can connect, discuss, share ideas, and support each other with their knowledge on a specific topic. Adding [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-forum-plugin-for-wordpress/\">12 Best Forum Plugins for WordPress Compared &#038; Reviewed</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - Free WordPress Theme Detector</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19325:\"<p>Do you want to create a forum for your WordPress website? </p>\n<p>Forums are online communities where like-minded people can communicate through conversational threads. </p>\n<p>It&#8217;s a wonderful platform to engage your audience in a two-way dialogue. Plus, community members can connect, discuss, share ideas, and support each other with their knowledge on a specific topic. </p>\n<p>Adding a forum to your website can have a lot of advantages for your business. You can use it to engage people with different conversations and encourage them to come back later to find your latest posts or updates about your business. </p>\n<p>By doing so, you not only increase your website traffic but also boost your sales and other conversion goals. The best way to add a forum to your website is by using a forum plugin. In this article, we&#8217;ll tell you about the best forum plugins that can help you create a forum without writing any code.</p>\n<p>But before that, let&#8217;s have a quick look at the benefits of adding a forum to your website. </p>\n<h3>Benefits of Adding a Forum to Your Website</h3>\n<p>As mentioned above, forums can help you get more traffic, increase your conversions, and boost sales on your website. But there are other benefits, such as: </p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Create User-Generated Content:</strong> With the help of a forum you can create <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-plugins-for-user-generated-content/\">user-generated content</a> for your visitors. This can come in the form of comments, reviews, images, or videos that others share. </li>\n<li><strong>Offer Support:</strong> Forums can be a great platform to offer customer support. You can create a discussion around any topic you want and categorize these topics. This makes it easy for your users to find information they&#8217;re looking for.</li>\n<li><strong>Create a Social Network:</strong> You can <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/social-networking-site-like-facebook/\">create a huge social network</a> of website users who can engage in different discussions, share ideas, and help solve each other&#8217;s problems.</li>\n<li><strong>SEO:</strong> Sometimes, forum threads have the most useful content unlike anything else on your site. This helps forums get to the top position in search results which can bring in lots of search traffic. This can have a big impact on the overall <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/complete-wordpress-seo-guide-beginners/\">SEO of your website</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Now, let&#8217;s check out some of the best forum plugins that can help you add a forum to your website. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/bbpress/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">1. bbPress</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/bbpress/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/bbPress.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"775\" height=\"351\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-247533\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/bbPress.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/bbPress-300x136.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/bbPress-768x348.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/bbpress/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">bbPress</a> is a free and open-source forum plugin that lets you create a forum for your entire website. It&#8217;s a responsive and light-weight solution that works beautifully with most standard WordPress themes without slowing down your site. </p>\n<p>The plugin is also compatible with other advanced WordPress plugins that you may use to expand your features. You can use it to create multi-site forums just like a professional would create for you. To help you get started quickly, it offers several customizable templates, each with tons of flexibility. bbPress is perfect for creating and managing custom forums.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/buddypress/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">2. BuddyPress</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/buddypress/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/BuddyPress.jpg\" alt=\"forum plugins\" width=\"775\" height=\"344\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-247537\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/BuddyPress.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/BuddyPress-300x133.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/BuddyPress-768x341.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/buddypress/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">BuddyPress</a> is a modern and robust forum plugin that lets you create a social networking site without any code. All you need to do is to install the plugin on your website, work on the customizations, and you&#8217;re good to go. </p>\n<p>Users can register on the site you make to create user profiles, have private conversations, make social connections, create and interact in groups, and much more. It offers powerful theme compatibility so you can use it with any theme of your choice. You can also download BuddyPress specific themes if you want. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/pricing/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">3. MonsterInsights</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/pricing/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/MonsterInsights.png\" alt=\"MonsterInsights, forum plugins\" width=\"775\" height=\"532\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-247534\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/MonsterInsights.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/MonsterInsights-300x206.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/MonsterInsights-768x527.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/pricing/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">MonsterInsights</a> is great analytics plugin that will help you track your forum users right from within your WordPress dashboard. You can use its advanced options to analyze the behavior of your forum members.  </p>\n<p>With MonsterInsights, you can also track your logged-in users vs non logged in users with custom dimensions. With the reports offered by this plugin, you can start making smart data-driven marketing decisions. </p>\n<p>You can learn <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/monsterinsights/\">more about MonsterInsights here</a>. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/pricing/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">4. WPForms</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/pricing/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms.jpg\" alt=\"WPForms, forum plugins, lead magnet plugin\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-222076\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/pricing/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WPForms</a> is a robust form builder plugin that helps you create custom login and registration forms for your forums without any coding. It offers a powerful drag and drop interface that makes it easy for you to design your forms. You can also use these forms for user registration on your forums. </p>\n<p>The instant notification feature can help you get notified every time there&#8217;s a new member request. This helps you take action instantly. </p>\n<p>You can also use spam protection and conditional logic in your forum forms for extra security. </p>\n<p>It integrates with several advanced <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-email-marketing-services-compared/\">email marketing services</a> like Mailchimp, AWeber, and others. With many other useful features, WPForms can be a great plugin for creating custom login forms for your forums. </p>\n<p>You can learn <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/wpforms/\">more about WPForms here</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://forumwpplugin.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">5. ForumWP</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://forumwpplugin.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/ForumWP.jpg\" alt=\"ForumWP\" width=\"775\" height=\"358\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-247521\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/ForumWP.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/ForumWP-300x139.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/ForumWP-768x355.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://forumwpplugin.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">ForumWP</a> is another amazing forum plugin that offers all the tools needed to build an online community for your business. It integrates beautifully with any theme you use adapting its button styles, fonts, and colors to blend effortlessly into your existing website. </p>\n<p>You can use it to add different forum layouts and give your forum a stunning look. It offers great control over who can view your forum. You can upload different images for each of your forums instead of icons, and it&#8217;s also easy for you to apply custom settings from the admin area. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/code-canyon-sabai-discuss/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >6. Sabai Discuss</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/code-canyon-sabai-discuss/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Sabai-Discuss.png\" alt=\"Sabai-Discuss\" width=\"775\" height=\"389\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-247522\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Sabai-Discuss.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Sabai-Discuss-300x151.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Sabai-Discuss-768x385.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/code-canyon-sabai-discuss/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Sabai Discuss</a> is a question and answer plugin for WordPress that can help you create a forum for your business website. If you&#8217;ve ever used Slack before, the interface of the forums created with this plugin will look familiar. </p>\n<p>Sabai Discuss is responsive and lets users filter questions and answers by custom fields. You can create search and filter forms using the visual form editor that the plugin offers. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/dw-question-answer-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >7. DW Question &#038; Answer Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/dw-question-answer-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DW-Question-Answer-Pro.png\" alt=\"DW-Question-Answer-Pro, forum plugins\" width=\"775\" height=\"386\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-247523\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DW-Question-Answer-Pro.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DW-Question-Answer-Pro-300x149.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DW-Question-Answer-Pro-768x383.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/dw-question-answer-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >DW Question &#038; Answer Pro</a> is another forum plugin that you can check out. The plugin is loaded with amazing features and it offers priority support, too. </p>\n<p>You can let your users manage the question and answers in the forum from the front-end itself. You can also add a voting system to your forum answers. The answers with the most votes will be saved as the best answer.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://simple-press.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">8. Simple:Press</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://simple-press.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Simple-Press.png\" alt=\"Simple-Press\" width=\"775\" height=\"292\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-247524\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Simple-Press.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Simple-Press-300x113.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Simple-Press-768x289.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>With <a href=\"https://simple-press.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Simple:Press</a> you can easily create forums, membership sites, and communities for your WordPress website. This SEO-friendly plugin is super secure and is cross-browser compatible. </p>\n<p>The forums you create with this plugin lets you add a private messaging feature to let users contact each other. The plugin also integrates well with other advanced plugins so you expand your forum features.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/asgaros-forum/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">9. Asgaros</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/asgaros-forum/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Asgaros-Forum.png\" alt=\"Asgaros-Forum, forum plugins\" width=\"775\" height=\"255\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-247525\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Asgaros-Forum.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Asgaros-Forum-300x99.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Asgaros-Forum-768x253.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/asgaros-forum/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Asgaros</a> is a free yet robust forum plugin that&#8217;s perfect for anyone who wants to have a forum for their WordPress website. The plugin is super light-weight, extremely fast, and secure for any kind of business. </p>\n<p>It integrates seamlessly with all plugins and themes that you use on your website. It also lets you monetize your forums by posting ads. As the admin of the forum, you can have total control over what gets displayed. You can also ban users from your dashboard if you want. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-discussion-board/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">10. Discussion Board</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-discussion-board/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Discussion-Board.jpg\" alt=\"forum plugins\" width=\"775\" height=\"339\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-247538\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Discussion-Board.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Discussion-Board-300x131.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Discussion-Board-768x336.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-discussion-board/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Discussion Board</a> is another forum plugin that simplifies the task of creating a forum for you website. It lets your users register and log in to the forum from the front-end. Users can post a new topic simply by submitting a form. </p>\n<p>Each of these topics will be reflected on the forum page, and users can post their replies on it. To protect your forum from spam, you can limit users from frequent reposting. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/cm-answers/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">11. CM Answers</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/cm-answers/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/CM-Answers--WordPress-plugin-WordPress-org.png\" alt=\"CM Answers\" width=\"775\" height=\"254\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-247528\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/CM-Answers--WordPress-plugin-WordPress-org.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/CM-Answers--WordPress-plugin-WordPress-org-300x98.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/CM-Answers--WordPress-plugin-WordPress-org-768x252.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/cm-answers/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">CM Answers</a> is another plugin that you can try out. With this plugin, you can create a question and answer forum that looks like the interface of Slack. The plugin offers you full control over how these forums work. </p>\n<p>You can enable or disable voting, moderate comments, enable notifications, and do a lot more. As an admin, you can also edit answers if you want. You&#8217;ll love its flexibility in terms of the being able to control your forums.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wpforo/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">12. wpForo Forum</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wpforo/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/wpForo-Forum--WordPress-plugin-WordPress-org.png\" alt=\"wpForo-Forum--WordPress-plugin-WordPress-org\" width=\"775\" height=\"249\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-247529\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/wpForo-Forum--WordPress-plugin-WordPress-org.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/wpForo-Forum--WordPress-plugin-WordPress-org-300x96.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/wpForo-Forum--WordPress-plugin-WordPress-org-768x247.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wpforo/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">wpForo Forum</a> is a free yet light-weight and responsive forum solution that is super easy to use. It offers various modern forum layouts to give your forum a professional look. </p>\n<p>It integrates seamlessly with many Profile Builder and Membership plugins, such as BuddyPress and Ultimate Members plugins. You can also migrate content from other existing forums very easily with wpForo Forum. </p>\n<p>And there you have it! We hope this article helps you pick the best plugin for creating your business forum. </p>\n<p>And if you like building community sites, you might also want to know <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-a-reddit-like-website/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">how to create a website like Reddit</a>. By creating an online community like Reddit, you can have a larger audience for your business. That can get you tons of traffic and help boost your conversion goals. </p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-forum-plugin-for-wordpress/\">12 Best Forum Plugins for WordPress Compared &#038; Reviewed</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - Free WordPress Theme Detector</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-forum-plugin-for-wordpress/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:50:\"19 Best Free eCommerce Themes for WordPress (2020)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-free-wordpress-ecommerce-themes/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-free-wordpress-ecommerce-themes/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 28 Jul 2020 05:16:39 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Resources\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"eCommerce free themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:24:\"free themesfor eCommerce\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"woocommerce themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=246629\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:614:\"<p>Are you looking for a good eCommerce theme for your WordPress website? The eCommerce market is growing and so is the competition between eCommerce websites. If you have an eCommerce site and want to grow, you need to ensure that your site looks amazing and functions smoothly. For that, you should make it user-friendly, visually [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-free-wordpress-ecommerce-themes/\">19 Best Free eCommerce Themes for WordPress (2020)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - Free WordPress Theme Detector</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31943:\"<p>Are you looking for a good eCommerce theme for your WordPress website? </p>\n<p>The eCommerce market is growing and so is the competition between eCommerce websites. If you <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-an-online-store-step-by-step/\">have an eCommerce site</a> and want to grow, you need to ensure that your site looks amazing and functions smoothly. </p>\n<p>For that, you should make it user-friendly, visually stunning, mobile responsive, and engaging. By doing so, you&#8217;ll not only attract more visitors but can also boost your conversions.</p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re just starting out, though, doing all of this at the same time can sound difficult. </p>\n<p>To make things easy for you, we&#8217;ve brought to you a list of fully responsive eCommerce themes with super impressive features. By using them, you can have the perfect look for your website without any coding skills required. </p>\n<p>We know that not everyone is willing to invest a lot of money right when they&#8217;re starting out. So we included many free themes in this list for you. </p>\n<p>Let&#8217;s get started. </p>\n<h3>Best Free eCommerce WordPress Themes </h3>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-mai-lifestyle-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >1. StudioPress</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-mai-lifestyle-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Studiopress-free-themes.jpg\" alt=\"Studiopress free themes, free ecommerce themes\" width=\"775\" height=\"392\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-246666\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Studiopress-free-themes.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Studiopress-free-themes-300x152.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Studiopress-free-themes-768x388.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-mai-lifestyle-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >StudioPress</a> is one of the most popular themes on the market. It&#8217;s a premium WordPress marketplace that offers beautiful themes for all kinds of websites. Plus, you can have all of them for free if you use <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpengine/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >WP Engine</a> as your web host. </p>\n<p>WP Engine is a leading managed WordPress hosting solution that offers fast website experience and cutting edge WordPress functionality. </p>\n<p>Check out this review to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/wpengine-review/\">learn more about WP Engine</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Features: </strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fast and lightweight</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-themes/genesis-theme-framework-review/\">Genesis Framework</a> Package</li>\n<li>Up to 3 column layouts</li>\n<li>35+ StudioPress Themes</li>\n<li>Pre-built homepages</li>\n<li>SEO-friendly</li>\n<li>And more</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-mai-lifestyle-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Get the StudioPress Themes Today!</a></p>\n<div class=\"alert alert-success\"><strong><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpengine/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >FREE ACCESS: All the Premium StudioPress Themes!</a></strong> </p>\n<p>Want to try all the premium StudioPress themes, for FREE?</p>\n<p>When you sign up for <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpengine/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >WP Engine</a>, the best managed WordPress hosting service, you receive the Genesis framework and ALL StudioPress themes for free (That&#8217;s over $2,000 in value!)</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpengine/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Get All 35+ Themes for FREE With WP Engine</a></div>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >2. Ultra</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Ultra-theme.png\" alt=\"Ultra theme, free eCommerce themes\" width=\"775\" height=\"438\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-246648\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Ultra-theme.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Ultra-theme-300x170.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Ultra-theme-768x434.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Ultra</a> is a multipurpose WordPress theme that looks great on all niche sites and can be a great fit for eCommerce stores too. It&#8217;s fully flexibile in terms of customization, so you can have full control of your design from the header to the footer. Plus, Ultra looks stunning across all screen sizes. </p>\n<p>Here&#8217;s a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-themes/themify-ultra/\">detailed review of Ultra</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Pre-built demo sites</li>\n<li>One-click demo setup</li>\n<li>60+ pre-designed layouts</li>\n<li>Different layout options</li>\n<li>Section scrolling</li>\n<li>WooCommerce integration</li>\n<li>And more</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Get the Ultra theme today!</a></p>\n<div class=\"alert alert-success\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Download the Ultra eCommerce theme for free</a> and change your store look instantly.</div>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/oceanwp/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >3. OceanWP</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/oceanwp/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/oceanwp-1.jpg\" alt=\"OceanWP, free eCommerce themes\" width=\"775\" height=\"440\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-245474\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/oceanwp-1.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/oceanwp-1-300x170.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/oceanwp-1-768x436.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/oceanwp/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >OceanWP</a> is a free multipurpose WordPress theme that&#8217;ll give your eCommerce site a stunning look without any coding. This theme is loaded with great features and is super easy to handle. </p>\n<p>It offers several pre-built demos that can be imported with just a single click. Read this detailed review to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-themes/oceanwp/\">learn more about OceanWP</a>. </p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Beautiful demo sites</li>\n<li>One-click demo import</li>\n<li>Native cart popup</li>\n<li>Floating add-to-cart bar</li>\n<li>Quick view</li>\n<li>Translation &#038; RTL ready</li>\n<li>And a lot more</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/oceanwp/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Get the OceanWP theme today!</a></p>\n<div class=\"alert alert-success\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/oceanwp/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Download the OceanWP eCommerce theme for free</a>. It&#8217;s fast, responsive and visually stunning.</div>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/astra-wordpress-theme/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >4. Astra</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/astra-wordpress-theme/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/astra-1.jpg\" alt=\"Astra theme, free ecommerce themes\" width=\"775\" height=\"440\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-245475\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/astra-1.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/astra-1-300x170.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/astra-1-768x436.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/astra-wordpress-theme/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Astra</a> is another free multipurpose WordPress theme that&#8217;s fast, light-weight, and fully customizable. It&#8217;s compatible with page builders which makes it super easy for you to create your sites with Astra. </p>\n<p>Read this <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-themes/astra/\">review of the Astra theme</a> to learn more. </p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Pixel perfect pre-built demos</li>\n<li>Seamless WooCommerce integration</li>\n<li>Translation &#038; RTL ready</li>\n<li>Unparalleled performance</li>\n<li>Blog &#038; Archive options</li>\n<li>Catchy storefront</li>\n<li>And a lot more</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/astra-wordpress-theme/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Get the Astra theme today!</a></p>\n<div class=\"alert alert-success\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/astra-wordpress-theme/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Download the beautiful Astra eCommerce theme for free</a>. You can also check out it&#8217;s <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/astra-pro-theme/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >premium version</a> if you want to try out it&#8217;s starter templates.</div>\n<h