png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Bellini_WordPress_theme-300x149.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Bellini_WordPress_theme-768x382.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/bellini/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Bellini</a> is a great eCommerce friendly theme that will look stunning on your store. It offers a responsive &#038; flexible layout that&#8217;s built with Bootstrap &#038; underscores.me. </p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Flexible layout</li>\n<li>SEO-friendly</li>\n<li>Custom colors</li>\n<li>Featured header image</li>\n<li> And much more</li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/bellini/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Get the Bellini theme today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/ecommerce-solution/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">19. eCommerce Solution</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/ecommerce-solution/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/eCommerce-solution.jpg\" alt=\"eCommerce solution\" width=\"775\" height=\"534\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-246663\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/eCommerce-solution.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/eCommerce-solution-300x207.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/eCommerce-solution-768x529.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/ecommerce-solution/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">eCommerce Solution</a> is a wonderful theme, which is perfect for eCommerce websites. It supports different languages, is super responsive, and cross-browser compatible too. </p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Site preloader option</li>\n<li>Related option</li>\n<li>Icon changer option</li>\n<li>Background image skin option</li>\n<li>Woocommerce options</li>\n<li>and a lot more</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/ecommerce-solution/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Get the eCommerce Solution theme today!</a></p>\n<p>These are some of the best and free eCommerce themes that can instantly make your store look more stunning and professional. We hope this article helps you find the best theme for your online store. </p>\n<p>Once you take care of your website&#8217;s appearance, you might also want to optimize it with other features to offer a better user experience and maximize your conversions. If you do, here&#8217;s a list of <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-woocommerce-plugins-grow-sales-rapidly/\">the best WooCommerce plugins</a> that you can choose from.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-free-wordpress-ecommerce-themes/\">19 Best Free eCommerce Themes for WordPress (2020)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - Free WordPress Theme Detector</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-free-wordpress-ecommerce-themes/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"9 Best Call to Action Plugins for WordPress in 2020\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-call-to-action-plugins-wordpress/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-call-to-action-plugins-wordpress/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 24 Jul 2020 18:37:37 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"WordPress Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"call to action plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"call to action wordpress plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"cta plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"cta wordpress plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=246526\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:610:\"<p>Are you looking for the best call to action plugins for your WordPress website? A call to action, popularly known as a CTA, is a well-designed button that prompts visitors to take certain actions on your website. These are actions like filling out a form, downloading a resource, buying a product, and more. If you&#8217;re [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-call-to-action-plugins-wordpress/\">9 Best Call to Action Plugins for WordPress in 2020</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - Free WordPress Theme Detector</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15504:\"<p>Are you looking for the best call to action plugins for your WordPress website? </p>\n<p>A call to action, popularly known as a CTA, is a well-designed button that prompts visitors to take certain actions on your website. These are actions like filling out a form, downloading a resource, buying a product, and more. </p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re a WordPress user who isn&#8217;t very &#8220;techy,&#8221; designing a good CTA can be tough. But don&#8217;t worry. WordPress offers many call to action plugins that let you build a CTA button quickly and easily. </p>\n<p>However, with such a huge list of options to choose from, picking the right plugin for your website can be confusing. </p>\n<p>That&#8217;s why we&#8217;ve put together a list of hand-picked plugins that you can use on your website. </p>\n<p>Let&#8217;s dive in! </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">1. OptinMonster</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Optinmonster-1.jpg\" alt=\"Optinmonster, best cta, best call to action plugin\" width=\"775\" height=\"384\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-246516\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Optinmonster-1.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Optinmonster-1-300x149.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Optinmonster-1-768x381.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">OptinMonster</a> is the most popular conversion optimization software that lets you add a CTA to your posts and pages without any code. Whether you want to get more leads, reduce shopping cart abandonment, or make an onsite retargeting offer, OptinMonster makes CTAs easy to set up. </p>\n<p>By doing so, you can distract your visitors with an offer that will both benefit and keep them on your website for longer. This is an excellent way of decreasing your bounce rates. </p>\n<p>You can add a CTA to your optin campaign that will prompt your users into action. OptinMonster uses its <strong>InactiveSensor</strong> feature to detect inactive visitors and convert them into subscribers. With its <strong>Campaign scheduling</strong> feature, you can easily run time-sensitive campaigns at the exact time and date that you want. </p>\n<p>These are just some of the many ways you can boost conversions with CTAs using OptinMonster.</p>\n<p>To learn more about OptinMonser, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/optinmonster/\">read this detailed review</a>. </p>\n<h2><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/beaver-builder/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >2. Beaver Builder</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/beaver-builder/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/beaver-builder.jpg\" alt=\"Beaver Builder\" width=\"775\" height=\"440\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-245812\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/beaver-builder.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/beaver-builder-300x170.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/beaver-builder-768x436.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/beaver-builder/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Beaver Builder</a> is a powerful <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-page-builders-compared/\">drag and drop page builder</a> plugin that lets you easily design your website. It offers several modules like images, heading, CTA buttons, and more that can be draged and dropped onto your page. </p>\n<p>Customizing these modules is easy too. You can add your CTA wherever you want it to appear and then add a nice color to it. You can link your button to other pages and change the font style and size of your button as well. Here&#8217;s a post on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-custom-wordpress-layouts/\">how to create a layout with Beaver Builder</a>. You can check out step 2 of this post to know how to add a call to action button. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/elementor-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >3. Elementor</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/elementor-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/elementor.jpg\" alt=\"Elementor\" width=\"775\" height=\"440\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-245814\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/elementor.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/elementor-300x170.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/elementor-768x436.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/elementor-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Elementor</a> is another drag and drop page builder plugin that offers great designing options for all website creators. Even if you&#8217;re a newbie, you can use Elementor to style your web pages just like a professional. </p>\n<p>Elementor offers several design elements that are highly customizable. You can add images, buttons, texts, videos, and a lot more with Elementor. CTAs and the overall layout built with Elementor look crisp and clear on all devices. It&#8217;s also compatible with all themes and works great with all plugins too. Here&#8217;s <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/elementor/\">more information about Elementor</a>.   </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">4. MonsterInsights</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/pricing/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/monsterinsights.png\" alt=\"MonsterInsights\" width=\"775\" height=\"250\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-217048\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/monsterinsights.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/monsterinsights-300x97.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/monsterinsights-768x248.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">MonsterInsights</a> is a powerful Google Analytics plugin for WordPress. Wondering why we&#8217;re talking about an analytics plugin in a CTA plugins post? Because with MonsterInsights, you can track your CTA button clicks right from your WordPress dashboard. </p>\n<p>All you need to do is <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/install-wordpress-plugin/\">install the plugin </a>on your website, <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/docs/connect-google-analytics/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">connect it to Google Analytics</a> and you&#8217;re ready to go. You can now track every detail of your website from your dashboard even without switching tabs. </p>\n<p>It offers real-time stats right within your dashboard. You can also automatically track clicks on your affiliate links, banner ads, and other outbound links. If you want to know detailed stats about your CTA and measure your click-through rates, this plugin is a must-have. Here&#8217;s a bit <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/monsterinsights/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">more information about MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-call-button/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">5. WP Call Button</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-call-button/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/WP-Call-Button.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"775\" height=\"262\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-240342\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/WP-Call-Button.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/WP-Call-Button-300x101.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/WP-Call-Button-768x260.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-call-button/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">WP Call Button</a> is a free plugin that lets you add a click to call button to your website. You can add floating call buttons that will scroll along with your visitor as they scroll down the page. This plugin has been designed to be mobile-friendly. So no matter which device it is viewed on, your click to call CTA will look equally stunning. </p>\n<p>You can also customize these buttons with your favorite color or add text and styles to them as well. With its optimized call button placement options, it&#8217;s easy to place anywhere you want on your website. Check out this post to learn <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/add-call-now-button-wordpress/\">how to use this button to add a call button to your site</a>. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://ultimateblocks.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">6. Ultimate Blocks</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ultimateblocks.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Ultimate_Blocks.png\" alt=\" plugin, cta plugins, call to action plugins\" width=\"775\" height=\"270\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-246531\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Ultimate_Blocks.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Ultimate_Blocks-300x105.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Ultimate_Blocks-768x268.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://ultimateblocks.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Ultimate Blocks</a> is a custom Gutenberg block plugin for bloggers and web designers that offers 18 essential blocks for your website. One of these blocks is the button. Apart from that, you can also add testimonials, image sliders to display multiple images, a countdown timer, a progress bar, and a lot more. </p>\n<p>To keep up your website performance, it offers the option to enable or disable individual blocks that you&#8217;re currently not using. Ultimate Blocks is SEO-friendly and super easy to use. You&#8217;ll love its flexibility and customization features.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://thrivethemes.com/affiliates/ref.php?id=4023&#038;url=6171\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" >7. Thrive Ultimatum</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://thrivethemes.com/affiliates/ref.php?id=4023&#038;url=6171\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Thrive_Ultimatum.png\" alt=\"Thrive_Ultimatum, cta plugin\" width=\"775\" height=\"337\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-246530\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Thrive_Ultimatum.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Thrive_Ultimatum-300x130.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Thrive_Ultimatum-768x334.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://thrivethemes.com/affiliates/ref.php?id=4023&#038;url=6171\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Thrive Ultimatum</a> is a scarcity marketing tool that lets you <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-add-social-proof-wordpress/\">create a sense of FOMO (fear of missing out)</a> to boost your conversions. This drag and drop builder comes with a range of professionally designed templates for countdown timers, widgets, buttons, and floating banners. </p>\n<p>It offers great customization options for your campaigns, so it&#8217;s easy to style your buttons to match your brand. Just click to edit any element, set custom colors, background images, custom fonts, and much more. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mythemeshop-wp-notification-bar-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >8. WP Notification Bar Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mythemeshop-wp-notification-bar-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/WP_Notification_Bar.png\" alt=\"WP_Notification_Bar pro, call to action buttons\" width=\"775\" height=\"371\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-246529\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/WP_Notification_Bar.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/WP_Notification_Bar-300x144.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/WP_Notification_Bar-768x368.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mythemeshop-wp-notification-bar-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >WP Notification Bar Pro</a> is actually a notification bar plugin that lets you add a button on your notification bar. Users can click on this button and take the action that you want them to. You can use this button to add unlimited bars on your site.</p>\n<p>To know which notification bar will bring you the best results, you can use its A/B testing feature and compare them side-by-side. With this plugin, you can also track the number of views and clicks on your notification bars and buttons. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/simple-side-tab/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">9. Simple Side Tab</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/simple-side-tab/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Simple_Side_Tab.jpg\" alt=\"CTA buttons\" width=\"775\" height=\"250\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-246528\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Simple_Side_Tab.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Simple_Side_Tab-300x97.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Simple_Side_Tab-768x248.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/simple-side-tab/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Simple Side Tab</a> is a free and user-friendly plugin that lets you add a CTA button on your website without any coding. The button added with this plugin will be placed on top of your site and stick around as your visitor scrolls down. You can place it on the right or left side of the browser window and customize it too. </p>\n<p>It offers unlimited colors for the buttons, 7 standard screen fonts, and lets you add links to them as well. Simple Side Tab is regularly updated and is SEO-friendly as well.</p>\n<p>These are some of the best call to action plugins for WordPress. And because you&#8217;re looking for CTA plugins, we thought you might also want to check out some <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-notification-bar-plugins/\">notification bar plugins</a> for your site, too. </p>\n<p>These plugins are great if you want to make a special announcement or offer a limited-time-only sale. You can use these plugins to display your message and make them stick at the top of your browser. That way, it&#8217;s the first thing a visitor notices, and you can increase conversion rates across your site. </p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-call-to-action-plugins-wordpress/\">9 Best Call to Action Plugins for WordPress in 2020</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - Free WordPress Theme Detector</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-call-to-action-plugins-wordpress/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:50:\"How to Create a Custom 404 Error Page in WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-custom-404-error-page-wordpress/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:77:\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-custom-404-error-page-wordpress/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 24 Jul 2020 14:35:24 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:3:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"WordPress Tutorials\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"404 error page\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"how to add 404 error page in wp\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=246802\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:579:\"<p>Are you trying to create a 404 error page in WordPress? A 404 error page is where your audience will land if they try to open or access a page that could not be found in the server. By displaying a 404 page, you basically let your visitors know that the page doesn&#8217;t exist. While [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-custom-404-error-page-wordpress/\">How to Create a Custom 404 Error Page in WordPress</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - Free WordPress Theme Detector</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17849:\"<p>Are you trying to create a 404 error page in WordPress? </p>\n<p>A 404 error page is where your audience will land if they try to open or access a page that could not be found in the server. By displaying a 404 page, you basically let your visitors know that the page doesn&#8217;t exist. </p>\n<p>While 404 error pages are great for letting your visitors know about the error that has occurred, it also has the potential to make you lose you visitors.</p>\n<p>That&#8217;s because the right 404 page can either hurt or help your user experience (UX).</p>\n<p>By designing this page correctly, you can strategically guide your users where to find the page that they&#8217;re looking for. This is an excellent way of retaining visitors on your website and decreasing your bounce rate rather than making them leave your site. </p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll show you how to design a 404 error page in the simplest way and without any coding required. </p>\n<p>We&#8217;ll also tell you what causes a 404 error and how to fix it. Towards the end, we&#8217;ll show you some of the best and inspirational 404 error page examples for you to check out before creating your page.  </p>\n<p>Feel free to use this table of contents to find the right section for you:</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"#causes\" title = \"What causes the 4040 error\">What Causes the 404 Error</li>\n<p></a></p>\n<li><a href=\"#fixes\" title = \"How to fix the 4040 error\">How to Fix the 404 Error</li>\n<p></a>  </p>\n<li><a href=\"#beaver\" title = \"how to design a 404 error page with Beaver Builder\">How to Design a 404 Error Page with Beaver Builder</li>\n<p></a>  </p>\n<li><a href=\"#inspire\" title = \"Best 404 Error Page Examples for Inspiration\"> Best 404 Error Page Examples for Inspiration</li>\n<p></a>\n</ol>\n<p>Let&#8217;s begin.</p>\n<h3 id =\"causes\">What Causes the 404 Error Page</h3>\n<p>Generally, a 404 error page is displayed when your visitors try to find content that has either been deleted, removed, or moved to another URL. </p>\n<p>But there can be other reasons when your visitors see this error message. For example: </p>\n<ol>\n<li>The URL slug of the searched page has been changed without proper redirection. So when looking for a page, your users find the original page with the original URL.</li>\n<li>The domain name that has been searched for doesn&#8217;t exist anymore. This is most likely because the user has entered the wrong URL</li>\n<li>The server responsible for the website is not running, or the connection is broken.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>And once you identify the problem, you&#8217;ll need to figure out how to fix it.</p>\n<h3 id=\"fixes\">How to Fix the 404 Error</h3>\n<p>Landing on a 404 error page can be frustrating. And that&#8217;s why you must know how to fix it. Here are some tips you can try if you ever see a 404 error page on yours or on someone else&#8217;s site. </p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Check for errors in the URL:</strong> The first thing to do is to check for errors in the URL. Make sure that the URL you&#8217;ve entered is correct and doesn&#8217;t contain any misspelled words, or have missing characters like a forward slash, hyphen, and so on.</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/clear-cache-wordpress-detailed-guide/\">Clear your browser cache and cookies</a>:</strong> This solution will work like magic if you can see the 404 error page only from a certain computer. In these cases, try deleting your browser cache as well as all the cookies for this site and try again.</li>\n<li><strong>Reload the page:</strong> Sometimes the solution to a 404 error page can be found simply by reloading your page. So, refresh your page to see if the page is working. </li>\n<li><strong>Check the directory levels:</strong> If the URL displaying the error has the following structure: example.com/Directory1/Directory2/Directory3, you can go back to a previous directory. For example, you can go to <strong>example.com/Directory1/Directory2/</strong> to check if the desired page can be found there. If it doesn&#8217;t work, then go back to another directory.</li>\n<li><strong>Contact the website directly:</strong> Another good step to finding a solution would be to contact the website directly. You&#8217;ll find the contact details somewhere on the homepage of the website. They should be able to tell you if they have completely removed the page.</li>\n<li><strong>Use the website search function:</strong> You can also use the search function of the website and enter one or more keywords you&#8217;re looking for to find the specific page you want. </li>\n</ol>\n<p>Now we&#8217;ll show you how to create a 404 error page for your website. This section is helpful for website owners who want to display this error page to their users.</p>\n<h3 id=\"beaver\">How to Design a 404 Error Page with Beaver Builder</h3>\n<p>To design the 404 error page in this tutorial, we&#8217;ll be using the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/beaver-builder/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Beaver Builder</a> page builder. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/beaver-builder/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/beaver-builder.jpg\" alt=\"Beaver Builder\" width=\"775\" height=\"440\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-245812\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/beaver-builder.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/beaver-builder-300x170.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/beaver-builder-768x436.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/beaver-builder/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\">Beaver Builder</a> is a powerful <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-page-builders-compared/\">drag and drop page builder plugin</a> that lets you create beautiful pages for your website, without needing to know any code. </p>\n<p>You can find out <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/beaver-builder/\">more about Beaver Builder in this detailed review</a>.</p>\n<p>Apart from the Beaver Builder plugin, you&#8217;ll also need the Beaver Themer to be installed on your website. Beaver Themer is an addon that makes designing web pages with Beaver Builder super easy and quick. You don&#8217;t need to install this addon separately. It comes packed with the premium version of the Beaver Builder plugin. All you need to do is activate it on your site.  </p>\n<h3>Step 1: Installing Beaver Builder on Your Website</h3>\n<p>To get started, you first need to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/install-wordpress-plugin/\">install and activate</a> the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/beaver-builder/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Beaver Builder plugin </a>on your WordPress website. </p>\n<p>When its installed and activated, go to <strong>Settings &raquo; Page Builder</strong>. Here you can enter the license key to enable support and receive updates. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/beaver-builder/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Beaver-Builder-settings.jpg\" alt=\"Beaver Builder settings\" width=\"600\" height=\"254\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-239969\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Beaver-Builder-settings.jpg 600w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Beaver-Builder-settings-300x127.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Next, you&#8217;ll have to activate the Beaver Themer addon. For that, go to your dashboard and click on <strong>Plugins &raquo; Installed Plugins</strong>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Activate-beaver-themer-1-min.png\" alt=\"activate Beaver Themer\" width=\"775\" height=\"394\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-246860\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Activate-beaver-themer-1-min.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Activate-beaver-themer-1-min-300x153.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Activate-beaver-themer-1-min-768x390.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Here, you&#8217;ll see the <strong>Beaver Themer</strong> addon. Just click on the <strong>Activate</strong> button for the addon to start working. Now you&#8217;re ready to create your custom 404 error page.</p>\n<h3>Step 2: Adding the Themer Layout</h3>\n<p>Now on your dashboard, go to <strong>Beaver Builder &raquo; Themer Layouts</strong>. And click on <strong>Add New</strong>. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/New-themer-layout.jpg\" alt=\"404 error page\" width=\"809\" height=\"463\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-246828\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/New-themer-layout.jpg 809w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/New-themer-layout-300x172.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/New-themer-layout-768x440.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 809px) 100vw, 809px\" /></p>\n<p>This will open a new screen where you&#8217;ll see fields to add your title and select the type and layout of your page. Add <strong>404 error page</strong> as your page title. For <strong>Layout</strong> select 404 from the drop-down. Now, click on the <strong>Add Themer Layout</strong> button.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Adding-404-error-page.jpg\" alt=\"Adding 404 error page\" width=\"670\" height=\"326\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-246829\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Adding-404-error-page.jpg 670w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Adding-404-error-page-300x146.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Adding-404-error-page-330x160.jpg 330w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px\" /></p>\n<p>You&#8217;ll see a new window on your screen. Here, click on the <strong>Launch Beaver Builder</strong>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Edit-with-Beaver-Builder.jpg\" alt=\"beaver themer\" width=\"657\" height=\"390\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-246830\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Edit-with-Beaver-Builder.jpg 657w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Edit-with-Beaver-Builder-300x178.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 657px) 100vw, 657px\" /></p>\n<p>Now you can start designing your 404 error page using the modules (images, links, buttons, and so on) offered by Beaver Builder. If you can&#8217;t see the modules, click on the <strong>+</strong> button on the top right corner of your screen. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Beaver-Builder-modules.jpg\" alt=\"Beaver Builder modules\" width=\"712\" height=\"500\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-246831\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Beaver-Builder-modules.jpg 712w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Beaver-Builder-modules-300x211.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 712px) 100vw, 712px\" /></p>\n<p>When you click on the button, it will display all the Beaver Builder modules that can be dragged and dropped in the visual editor to create your 404 error page. The <strong>+</strong> sign will change to across sign just like in the image above. </p>\n<p>For more help, you can check out this detailed post on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-custom-wordpress-layouts/\">how to add modules to your Beaver page here</a>. You can use the modules, add images and links, and make it colorful and engaging for your users. </p>\n<h3>Step 3: Publishing Your 404 Error Page</h3>\n<p>Now that you&#8217;re done creating your page, click on the <strong/>Done</strong> button on the top right corner of your page. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/404_Error_Page-done-1.jpg\" alt=\"404_Error_Page done\" width=\"775\" height=\"297\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-246861\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/404_Error_Page-done-1.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/404_Error_Page-done-1-300x115.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/404_Error_Page-done-1-768x294.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>This will show you the <strong>Publish</strong> button. Click on it. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Publish-404_Error_Page-1.jpg\" alt=\"Publish 404_Error_Page\" width=\"775\" height=\"387\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-246862\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Publish-404_Error_Page-1.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Publish-404_Error_Page-1-300x150.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Publish-404_Error_Page-1-768x384.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Your 404 error page will now be live. Anyone who clicks on a broken link will see this page. </p>\n<p>And that&#8217;s it! You&#8217;re 404 page is ready to go. Easy, right? </p>\n<p>Now let&#8217;s see some great examples of 404 pages that you can use for extra inspiration when designing your own. </p>\n<h3 id=\"inspire\">Best 404 Error Page Examples for Inspiration</h3>\n<p>To help you design your 404 error page better, we&#8217;ve brought you some examples for inspiration. </p>\n<h3>1. Themeisle 404 Error Page</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Themeisle-404-error-page.png\" alt=\"Themeisle 404 error page\" width=\"775\" height=\"571\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-246850\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Themeisle-404-error-page.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Themeisle-404-error-page-300x221.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Themeisle-404-error-page-768x566.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Themeisle&#8217;s 404 error page is not only visually attractive but also offers a solution to the visitors to find what they were looking for. It added a search field to its page where visitors can enter one or more keywords of the page they wanted to visit. </p>\n<p>This a great way to retain your users and direct them to a place where they originally intended to be.  </p>\n<h3>2. 404 Error Page by Andrew Colling</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/404-error-by-Andrew-Collin.jpeg\" alt=\"404 error by Andrew Collin\" width=\"775\" height=\"581\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-246851\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/404-error-by-Andrew-Collin.jpeg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/404-error-by-Andrew-Collin-300x225.jpeg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/404-error-by-Andrew-Collin-768x576.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Andrew&#8217;s 404 error page is another example that can inspire you. It adds a beautiful graphic that resonates with the description added just below the title and humorously tries to redirect its visitors back to the homepage. It added a catchy call to action (CTA) button to direct people to a page where they can navigate through the website. </p>\n<h3>3. 404 Error Page by Ryan Duffy</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/404-erro-by-Ryan-Duffy.jpeg\" alt=\"404 erro by Ryan Duffy, inspiring 404 error page\" width=\"775\" height=\"581\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-246852\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/404-erro-by-Ryan-Duffy.jpeg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/404-erro-by-Ryan-Duffy-300x225.jpeg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/404-erro-by-Ryan-Duffy-768x576.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Ryan Duffy&#8217;s design is a simple yet powerful one. It tells its visitors that just like an accident, landing on the 404 error page is unintentional. But at the same time, it also shows them a way out of that page by using the CTA back to the homepage.  </p>\n<h3>4. 404 Error Page by Matt</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/404-error-by-Matt.png\" alt=\"404 error by Matt\" width=\"775\" height=\"581\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-246853\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/404-error-by-Matt.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/404-error-by-Matt-300x225.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/404-error-by-Matt-768x576.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>This page is different from the others mentioned above. It not only tells its visitors that the page doesn&#8217;t exist but also offers different solutions. It adds different links in the header that can help the visitor go to the other sections of the website. </p>\n<p>This is actually a great way of engaging your visitor because you&#8217;re giving them different options, so they are free to choose what they want to do. </p>\n<p>And that is how you create a 404 error page in WordPress. We hope this article helps you create a beautiful 404 error page for your site. </p>\n<p>Once you&#8217;re done creating your error page, you might want to check out a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-404-error-plugins/\">few plugins that can help you find and fix broken links</a> easily on your website.</p>\n<p>This will help you increase UX by getting rid of dead or broken links on your site.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-custom-404-error-page-wordpress/\">How to Create a Custom 404 Error Page in WordPress</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - Free WordPress Theme Detector</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-custom-404-error-page-wordpress/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"How to Create a Review Site in WordPress (that Make Money) in 2020\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-a-review-website/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-a-review-website/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 23 Jul 2020 01:40:43 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"WordPress Tutorials\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"affiliate marketing\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"refer products\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"review website\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=221162\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:609:\"<p>Do you want to create a review site in WordPress? Most people look for reviews before purchasing something online, which is why review websites are very popular on the internet. Plus, creating your own review website is one of the best ways to make money with affiliate marketing. In this article, we will show you [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-a-review-website/\">How to Create a Review Site in WordPress (that Make Money) in 2020</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - Free WordPress Theme Detector</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21893:\"<p>Do you want to create a review site in WordPress?</p>\n<p>Most people look for reviews before purchasing something online, which is why review websites are very popular on the internet.</p>\n<p>Plus, creating your own review website is one of the best ways to make money with affiliate marketing. </p>\n<p>In this article, we will show you how to create a review site in WordPress and earn a profit like a pro.</p>\n<h3>What Is a Review Website?</h3>\n<p>A review website is a content-based website aimed at generating affiliate revenue by publishing product reviews in a well-defined niche (like mobile phones or video games, for example).</p>\n<p>To create a review website, you&#8217;ll have to choose a specific niche, publish product reviews, and refer affiliate products in that niche. You&#8217;ll get paid whenever someone makes a purchase from your referral links.</p>\n<p>The easiest way to find products you want to promote is joining an affiliate program like<a href=\"http://www.wpbeginner.com/refer/shareasale/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">ShareASale</a>, <a href=\"https://affiliate-program.amazon.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Amazon Associates</a> or<a href=\"http://www.cj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Commission Junction</a>and browse through their product lists.</p>\n<p>After selecting a product you want to share, you can get an affiliate link and promote the product through a link on your site.</p>\n<p><strong>Read more:</strong> <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-plugins-for-affiliate-marketers/\">Best Affiliate Plugins for WordPress</a>.</p>\n<h3>Requirements for Building a Review Website</h3>\n<p>To build a review website, you&#8217;ll need the following things:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>A domain name</strong>: the web address of your website such as <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/\">IsItWP.com</a> or Google.com.</li>\n<li><strong>Web hosting</strong>: where your website files are stored.</li>\n<li><strong>WordPress plugins</strong>: tools that add features and new functionality to your WordPress site. We recommend using the following WordPress plugins for your review website.</li>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mythemeshop-wp-review/\" title=\"WP Review Pro\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">WP Review Pro</a>: A powerful and feature-rich WordPress review plugin with multiple rating systems.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/thirstyaffiliates/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">ThirstyAffiliates</a>: The best affiliate link management plugin.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://monsterinsights.com/\" target=\"_blank\">MonsterInsights</a>: The best Google Analytics plugin. It also gives you insights into how well your affiliate links are performing on your site.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WPForms</a>: The <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-contact-form-plugins/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Contact Form Plugins\">best WordPress form plugin</a> that also lets you publish user-generated reviews on your review website.</li>\n</ul>\n</ul>\n<p>With all that in mind, let&#8217;s look at how you can build a review site and generate profit through affiliate marketing.</p>\n<h3>Step 1: Set Up a WordPress Review Website</h3>\n<p>We always recommend using WordPress to set up a review website. WordPress is the most popular website builder in the world.</p>\n<p>It gives you endless possibilities to build and customize your website. For more details, you should check out our complete <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-review/\" title=\"WordPress Review: MUST Read Before Launching a Site\">WordPress review</a> and an in-depth resource explaining why you should use WordPress.</p>\n<p>To build a review website with WordPress, you&#8217;ll need to purchase a domain name and web hosting plan.</p>\n<p>We recommend <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bluehost</a> for hosting your WordPress website. It&#8217;s one of the largest hosting providers in the world and an officially recommended hosting provider by WordPress.org.</p>\n<p>Read our complete <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/bluehost-review/\" title=\"Bluehost\">Bluehost review</a> for more details.</p>\n<p>For IsItWP users, Bluehost offers a special deal, including a free domain name, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/get-free-ssl-certificate/\" title=\"How to Get a Free SSL Certificate in Minutes (HTTPS)\">free SSL certificate</a>, and 65% OFF on WordPress hosting.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/bluehost.jpg\" alt=\"Bluehost\" width=\"775\" height=\"440\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247156\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/bluehost.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/bluehost-300x170.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/bluehost-768x436.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Click Here to Claim This Exclusive Bluehost Offer &raquo;</a></p>\n<p>For more details, you should read our article on how to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\">make a website</a> with WordPress.</p>\n<p>Also, don&#8217;t miss this guide on the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/\" title=\"10 Best Web Hosting Companies for Small Businesses\">best web hosting</a> companies on the market.</p>\n<h3>Step 2: Transform Your Typical Website Into a Product Review Site</h3>\n<p>Next, you&#8217;ll need to install and activate the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mythemeshop-wp-review/\" title=\"WP Review Pro\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">WP Review Pro</a> plugin. It comes with multiple rating systems and built-in templates to showcase user reviews on your website.</p>\n<p>Some of the key features of WP Review Pro plugin are:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Rich Snippets:</strong> WP Review Pro supports multiple types of rich snippets. Plus, you can select a perfect snippet for your reviews in just a few clicks.</li>\n<li><strong>Google, Yelp, and Facebook Reviews:</strong> It seamlessly integrates with Google Places Reviews, Yelp Reviews, and Facebook Reviews to display user reviews from any social site.</li>\n<li><strong>Advanced Options Panel:</strong> It comes with a beginner-friendly options panel to configure and set up WordPress reviews without editing any code.</li>\n<li><strong>Translation Ready:</strong> The plugin is fully translatable so you can easily translate the reviews into any language.</li>\n<li><strong>Custom Widgets:</strong> It offers 10 custom widgets to add user reviews to your sidebar, footer, and other widget areas.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>For help using these plugins, you should check out our complete article on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/install-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"How to Install a WordPress Plugin  3 Methods (Step by Step)\">how to install a WordPress plugin</a>.</p>\n<p>After you activate these plugins, you need to go to the <strong>Settings &raquo; WP Review Pro</strong> page in your WordPress admin area. In the <strong>Global</strong> settings, you need to visit the <strong>General</strong> tab.</p>\n<p>Under this tab, you can manage general settings that include restricting ratings to registered users, adding a total rating to thumbnail, enabling user ratings in old posts, and so on.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/global-review-settings.jpg\" alt=\"Global Settings - General\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247232\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/global-review-settings.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/global-review-settings-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/global-review-settings-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Now you need to go to the <strong>Styling</strong> tab. From here, you can select the review style in the drop-down menu.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/global-styling-settings.jpg\" alt=\"Global - Styling Review\" width=\"775\" height=\"460\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247233\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/global-styling-settings.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/global-styling-settings-300x178.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/global-styling-settings-768x456.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>It shows you a preview in real-time of how your review will look. This makes it easier for you to select the best review style for your website.</p>\n<p>On this page, you can also change the colors of fonts, buttons, header background, border, and more.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/styling-color-settings.jpg\" alt=\"Styling Color Settings\" width=\"775\" height=\"460\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247234\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/styling-color-settings.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/styling-color-settings-300x178.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/styling-color-settings-768x456.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Next, you need to visit the <strong>Defaults</strong> tab to select review type, review location, review schema, features, links, and more.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/default-review-settings.jpg\" alt=\"Default Review Settings\" width=\"775\" height=\"440\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247235\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/default-review-settings.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/default-review-settings-300x170.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/default-review-settings-768x436.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>After that, go to the <strong>Embed</strong> tab to enable embed code, show titles, show thumbnails, and display other features.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/embed-review-settings.jpg\" alt=\"Embed Review Settings\" width=\"775\" height=\"440\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247236\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/embed-review-settings.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/embed-review-settings-300x170.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/embed-review-settings-768x436.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>You can also customize some of these settings for each post separately. Click on the <strong>Save Changes</strong> button to store your settings.</p>\n<p>In the <strong>Popup</strong> settings, you can enable a popup to display on page loads. You can also set the time (in seconds) to show a popup to users.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/popup-settings.jpg\" alt=\"Popup Settings\" width=\"775\" height=\"440\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247238\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/popup-settings.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/popup-settings-300x170.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/popup-settings-768x436.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Next, visit the <strong>Notification Bar</strong> settings. On this page, you can enable the notification bar and call-to-action button to display a notification bar on each page or post of your website.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/notification-bar-settings.jpg\" alt=\"Notification Bar Settings\" width=\"775\" height=\"440\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247239\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/notification-bar-settings.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/notification-bar-settings-300x170.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/notification-bar-settings-768x436.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>In the <strong>Styling</strong> tab, you can also manage the notification bar position, background color, text color, star color, and button colors.</p>\n<p>For third-party reviews, go to the <strong>Yelp Reviews</strong> setting and enter an API Key to integrate Yelp reviews on your website.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/yelp-reviews-integration.jpg\" alt=\"Yelp Reviews Integration\" width=\"775\" height=\"440\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247251\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/yelp-reviews-integration.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/yelp-reviews-integration-300x170.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/yelp-reviews-integration-768x436.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>You can do the same process for Google Place Reviews and Facebook Reviews. Don&#8217;t forget to click on the <strong>Save Changes</strong> button.</p>\n<p>If you want to import reviews from other WordPress plugins, then visit the <strong>Import Reviews</strong> section and select the plugin from the drop-down menu.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/import-reviews-setting.jpg\" alt=\"Import Reviews Setting\" width=\"775\" height=\"440\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247252\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/import-reviews-setting.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/import-reviews-setting-300x170.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/import-reviews-setting-768x436.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Make sure you click on the <strong>Save Changes</strong> button each time you update a setting.</p>\n<h3>Step 3: Publish Reviews in WordPress</h3>\n<p>Publishing reviews is easy with the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mythemeshop-wp-review/\" title=\"WP Review Pro\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">WP Review Pro</a> plugin.</p>\n<p>In your page or post editor, you&#8217;ll find a meta box called <strong>Review</strong>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/review-box.jpg\" alt=\"Review Box\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247254\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/review-box.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/review-box-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/review-box-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>If you don&#8217;t change any settings here, then it will display the user review based on your default settings. However, you can change a lot of settings on each page or post to display a unique user review section.</p>\n<p>Once you&#8217;re done, you can publish your post.</p>\n<p>The review box will appear on the page or post of your website. It shows the heading, review count, and review type (star, point, percentage, and so on).</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/review-box-preview.jpg\" alt=\"Review Box Preview\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247256\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/review-box-preview.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/review-box-preview-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/review-box-preview-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<h3>Recommended Plugins for Creating a Review Website</h3>\n<p>We highly recommend that you install the following WordPress plugins on your review website.</p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/thirstyaffiliates/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. ThirstyAffiliates</a></strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/thirstyaffiliates/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/thirstyaffiliates.jpg\" alt=\"ThirstyAffiliates\" width=\"775\" height=\"250\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-217285\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/thirstyaffiliates.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/thirstyaffiliates-300x97.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/thirstyaffiliates-768x248.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/thirstyaffiliates/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">ThirstyAffiliates</a> is the best affiliate link management plugin. It lets you easily organize your affiliate links in a single location, so you can insert affiliate links into your articles directly from your post editor.</p>\n<p>When you organize all of your affiliate links in a single place, you can quickly find and replace the links without any hassle.</p>\n<p>This comes in handy, especially when the company you promote modifies the affiliate link that youve added to your articles. You don&#8217;t have to dig through every blog post you&#8217;ve published to find and replace the affiliate links. </p>\n<p>Instead, you can simply replace the affiliate link in your WordPress admin. This will automatically change the links inserted on all of your posts.</p>\n<p>The plugin also lets you cloak your affiliate links so you can turn your ugly affiliate links into pretty links. Not only does this make your links look nicer to users, it helps prevent hackers from hijacking your affiliate commissions.</p>\n<p>Read our complete <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/thirstyaffiliates/\">ThirstyAffiliates review</a> for more information.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/thirstyaffiliates/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with ThirstyAffiliates!</a></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\" target=\"_blank\">2. MonsterInsights</a></strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/monsterinsights.png\" alt=\"MonsterInsights\" width=\"775\" height=\"250\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-217048\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/monsterinsights.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/monsterinsights-300x97.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/monsterinsights-768x248.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\" target=\"_blank\">MonsterInsights</a> is the best Google Analytics plugin for WordPress. With MonsterInsights, you can easily set up Google Analytics, and even enable affiliate link tracking on your site.</p>\n<p>By enabling affiliate link tracking, you can understand what works best for your audience. It can also give you insights into how to optimize your review site for boosting affiliate commissions.</p>\n<p>By tracking the clicks on your affiliate links, you can figure out the:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Most profitable traffic sources</li>\n<li>Top earning pages in your website</li>\n<li>Type of content that works best for generating affiliate revenue</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Get started with MonsterInsights!</a></p>\n<p>Read our complete <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/monsterinsights/\">MonsterInsights review</a>.</p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\">3. WPForms</a></strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/wpforms.png\" alt=\"WPForms\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-218485\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/wpforms.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/wpforms-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/wpforms-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WPForms</a> is the best contact form plugin for WordPress. This plugin makes it easy to build any type of online form with ease, like payment forms, login forms, and more.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WPForms</a> allows users to leave reviews on your WordPress site. With its post submission feature, you can create a frontend post submission form. When a user fills out the form, the entry will be submitted to your WordPress admin as a post or page for your review. That way you can review the submitted entries and then publish them.</p>\n<p>Also, check out this full comparison between <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/typeform-alternatives-wpforms-vs-typeform/\" title=\"TypeForm Alternatives: WPForms vs. TypeForm (Compared)\">WPForms vs. TypeForm</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/wpforms/\">Get started with WPForms!</a></p>\n<p>Or you can read the complete <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/wpforms/\">WPForms review</a>.</p>\n<p>That&#8217;s it!</p>\n<p>We hope this guide helped you create an awesome review site in WordPress.</p>\n<p>If you enjoyed this article, then you may also want to check out our guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-a-micro-job-site-like-fiverr/\" title=\"How to Create a Micro Job Site Like Fiverr (Step by Step)\">how to create a micro job site like Fiverr</a> to create job opportunities for your users.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-a-review-website/\">How to Create a Review Site in WordPress (that Make Money) in 2020</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - Free WordPress Theme Detector</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-a-review-website/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"8\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"10 Best Lightbox Plugins for WordPress (Compared &amp; Reviewed)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-lightbox-plugins-wordpress/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-lightbox-plugins-wordpress/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 22 Jul 2020 18:22:38 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"WordPress Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"lightbox plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"lightbox popup plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"wordpress popup plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=247170\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:626:\"<p>Are you looking for a lightbox plugin for your WordPress website? Adding a lightbox popup to your website is a very effective way of increasing your conversion rates. It helps you remove all distractions from your visitor&#8217;s screen by highlighting a single piece of content or call to action. So instead of being distracted by [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-lightbox-plugins-wordpress/\">10 Best Lightbox Plugins for WordPress (Compared &#038; Reviewed)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - Free WordPress Theme Detector</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16988:\"<p>Are you looking for a lightbox plugin for your WordPress website?</p>\n<p>Adding a lightbox popup to your website is a very effective way of increasing your conversion rates. It helps you remove all distractions from your visitor&#8217;s screen by highlighting a single piece of content or call to action.  </p>\n<p>So instead of being distracted by the other information on your site, your visitors can totally concentrate on what you want them to see. </p>\n<p>This is a great way of <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-content-upgrade/\">optimizing your conversion goals</a>. </p>\n<p>You can use lightbox popups to promote a product, highlight a sale, increase your subscribers, or any other action you want your site&#8217;s visitors to take. </p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll tell you about the top lightbox plugins for WordPress that you can use on your website. But before that, let&#8217;s make sure we&#8217;re on the same page as to what a lightbox is and why you need to use them. </p>\n<h3>What Is a Lightbox and Why Use It</h3>\n<p>A lightbox is a popup window that can be displayed on your website to show users a message or promotional deal. You can use these popups to display images, videos, special offers, or anything that you want them to notice. </p>\n<p>Lightboxes typically come in 2 forms:</p>\n<ul>\n<li> Popups</li>\n<li> Image/Video galleries</li>\n</ul>\n<p>But both work in the same way. When you display a lightbox on your website, the rest of the screen becomes darker, and the user&#8217;s eye naturally goes to your image or text.  </p>\n<p>This makes it perfectly clear what you want users to see or do next, which is why it&#8217;s a great conversion optimization tool for your business. </p>\n<p>These popups can also engage your visitors with something different from what they were previously looking at. It&#8217;s a great way of retaining them on your site for longer and enticing them to explore new content. This will also help you reduce your bounce rate, which, in turn, improves your SEO efforts.</p>\n<p>Now, let&#8217;s check out some of the best lightbox plugins for your WordPress website. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/pricing/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">1. OptinMonster</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/pricing/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/optinmonster.png\" alt=\"OptinMonster, marketing automation tools\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-243532\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/optinmonster.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/optinmonster-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/optinmonster-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/pricing/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">OptinMonster</a> is the most powerful customer acquisition and lead generation software on the market. It lets you create beautiful lightboxes without any coding. </p>\n<p>It also offers great features to make sure your popups stand out. You can display the popups in the form of a lightbox, a floating bar, an inline form, fullscreen overlays, side scroll-in boxes, and more. </p>\n<p>To help you get started quickly, OptinMonster provides you with over 50 pre-built templates. Each of these templates is ready to be used and is fully customizable. Their drag and drop builder makes the plugin super flexible in terms of any customization you want to do. </p>\n<p>Plus, with its advanced targeting features, you get to control when, where, and to whom your pop appears.  </p>\n<p>Check out this detailed review to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/optinmonster/\">learn more about OptinMonster</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeisle-nivo-slider/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >2. Nivo Slider</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeisle-nivo-slider/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Nivo-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"Nivo slider plugin\" width=\"775\" height=\"396\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247223\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Nivo-plugin.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Nivo-plugin-300x153.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Nivo-plugin-768x392.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeisle-nivo-slider/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Nivo Slider</a> is another WordPress plugin that lets you add beautiful sliders to your website. Each of these sliders is fully customizable. You can use them to showcase your images, blogs, galleries, or anything else that you want to display. </p>\n<p>The plugin works beautifully with all themes and other plugins that you may have installed. That means you don&#8217;t have to change anything to use it. You can create your sliders from your media galleries and blog posts too. </p>\n<p>You don&#8217;t need any professional skills to use this plugin. It&#8217;s super handy, so you can easily use it on your site.   </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/nextgen-gallery/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >3. NexGen Gallery</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/nextgen-gallery/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/NextGEN_Pro.jpg\" alt=\"NextGEN_Pro, lightbox plugins\" width=\"775\" height=\"306\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247048\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/NextGEN_Pro.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/NextGEN_Pro-300x118.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/NextGEN_Pro-768x303.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/nextgen-gallery/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >NextGen Gallery</a> is a wonderful lightbox plugin for photographers and other creative minds who want to display their work in an impressive way. It offers you 12 different gallery types to make your images look unique. You can also choose whether you want to allow commenting on these images or not. </p>\n<p>To protect the images from theft, it offers the image protection feature. You can also show your captions whenever a visitor hovers over the images. NextGen is ready for <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-ecommerce-plugins-compared/\">eCommerce</a> too. To easily accept payments, it supports various payment options like PayPal, Stripe, and others. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/fooplugins/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >4. FooBox</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/fooplugins/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/fooplugins.jpg\" alt=\"FooPlugins, lightbox plugin\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-238955\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/fooplugins.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/fooplugins-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/fooplugins-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/fooplugins/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >FooBox</a> is another lightbox plugin that lets you add responsive media lightboxes to your WordPress website. With this plugin, you can let your visitors share your lightboxes on social platforms to attract more traffic. </p>\n<p>You can also use these lightboxes to share video content. The videos can be opened from popular hosting sites like YouTube and Vimeo. All your images and videos can be displayed in the form of a gallery. To make it easier for your visitors to view your content, you can also enable the auto-play option. </p>\n<p><H3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/code-canyon-image-map-hotspot-lightbox/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >5. Image Map HotSpot</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/code-canyon-image-map-hotspot-lightbox/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Image_Map_HotSpot.png\" alt=\"Image_Map_HotSpot\" width=\"775\" height=\"391\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247229\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Image_Map_HotSpot.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Image_Map_HotSpot-300x151.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Image_Map_HotSpot-768x387.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/code-canyon-image-map-hotspot-lightbox/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Image Map HotSpot</a> is another lightbox plugin that lets you display a popup when users click or hover over your maps. Visitors can easily drag the icon and drop it in their actual positions on the map.</p>\n<p>It offers 4 different popup styles. You can display it in the top, bottom, left, or right of where the visitor is positioned in the map. The plugin is easy to handle, and it supports images too. Plus, it looks good on all screen sizes. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/code-canyon-popup-plugin-wordpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >6. Popup Plugin for WorPress</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/code-canyon-popup-plugin-wordpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Popup_Plugin_for_WordPress.png\" alt=\"Popup_Plugin_for_WordPress\" width=\"775\" height=\"394\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247243\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Popup_Plugin_for_WordPress.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Popup_Plugin_for_WordPress-300x153.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Popup_Plugin_for_WordPress-768x390.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/code-canyon-popup-plugin-wordpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Popup Plugin for WordPress</a> is a great option when it comes to adding lightbox popups to your website. You can use these popups to highlight important content on your site.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-video-lightbox/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">7. WP Video Lightbox</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-video-lightbox/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WP_Video_Lightbox.png\" alt=\"WP_Video_Lightbox\" width=\"1240\" height=\"423\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247245\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WP_Video_Lightbox.png 1240w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WP_Video_Lightbox-300x102.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WP_Video_Lightbox-768x262.png 768w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WP_Video_Lightbox-1024x349.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1240px) 100vw, 1240px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-video-lightbox/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">WP Video Lightbox</a> is a lightbox plugin that lets you embed videos on your website in the form of responsive popups. You can also use it to display your images, YouTube &#038; Vimeo videos, and more in a lightbox overlay. </p>\n<p>To make your popup more engaging, it supports animation too. You can work on the speed of these animations to make it slow, fast, or normal. It even lets you auto-play your sliders so that you can set your own slider timing. </p>\n<p>Apart from that, WP Video Lightbox offers different themes for your lightbox, so you don&#8217;t need to design it from scratch.   </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-featherlight/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">8. WP Featherlight</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-featherlight/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WP_Featherlight.png\" alt=\"WP_Featherlight\" width=\"775\" height=\"245\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247246\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WP_Featherlight.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WP_Featherlight-300x95.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/WP_Featherlight-768x243.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-featherlight/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">WP Featherlight </a> is a super light and responsive lightbox plugin that makes it easy to add lightbox popups to your website. When you install the plugin on your website, it will automatically display all standard WordPress images and galleries in a simple, minimalistic lightbox popup style.</p>\n<p>It also lets you add lightbox videos, iframes, and ajax content with WP Featherlight by adding data attributes to your content. You don&#8217;t need any configuration for this plugin. Just install it, and you&#8217;re good to go.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/simply-gallery-block/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">9. Simply Gallery Blocks</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/simply-gallery-block/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Simply-Gallery_Blocks.png\" alt=\"Simply Gallery_Blocks\" width=\"775\" height=\"242\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247250\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Simply-Gallery_Blocks.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Simply-Gallery_Blocks-300x94.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Simply-Gallery_Blocks-768x240.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/simply-gallery-block/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Simply Gallery Blocks</a> is another amazing lightbox plugin that lets you display images from your posts and pages in the form of a customizable lightbox. The plugin is compatible with the latest version of WordPress. </p>\n<p>This plugin works wonders for photographers, artists, writers, content marketers, or any creative person who wants to display their work in a unique way. The plugin supports automatic slideshow and multi-touch support. You can also attach captions and alt tags to your images. To make your work visible to more people, you can also add social share buttons for easily enabling sharing. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/media-slider/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">10. Media Slider</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/media-slider/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Media-Slider.png\" alt=\"Media Slider\" width=\"775\" height=\"252\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-247255\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Media-Slider.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Media-Slider-300x98.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Media-Slider-768x250.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/media-slider/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Media Slider</a> is a free lightbox plugin that lets you create beautiful and responsive sliders for your images, videos and written content. Using this plugin, you can also add multiple media files to your sliders. </p>\n<p>It lets you create your sliders directly from the plugin admin dashboard, and you can copy the slider generated shortcode to the page where you want to display it. </p>\n<p>And there you have it! These are some of the best lightbox plugins that you can try out on your website. </p>\n<p>We hope this article helps you find the best lightbox plugin so you can create some really cool and unique popups for your visitors. </p>\n<p>But as your site becomes more popular, you may want to make your site safer for your users. For that, you should check out this resource on the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-security-plugins-compared/\">best security plugins</a>. </p>\n<p>This resource has everything you need to make your site more secure as your content gets more popular. </p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-lightbox-plugins-wordpress/\">10 Best Lightbox Plugins for WordPress (Compared &#038; Reviewed)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - Free WordPress Theme Detector</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-lightbox-plugins-wordpress/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:28:\"https://www.isitwp.com/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"hourly\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:15:\"updateFrequency\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}}}}s:4:\"type\";i:128;s:7:\"headers\";O:42:\"Requests_Utility_CaseInsensitiveDictionary\":1:{s:7:\"\0*\0data\";a:19:{s:6:\"server\";s:17:\"Sucuri/Cloudproxy\";s:4:\"date\";s:29:\"Wed, 05 Aug 2020 12:44:29 GMT\";s:12:\"content-type\";s:34:\"application/rss+xml; charset=UTF-8\";s:11:\"x-sucuri-id\";s:5:\"15003\";s:11:\"host-header\";s:40:\"e172abecbd394f56a1a2479517f27fbfe05ff815\";s:16:\"x-xss-protection\";s:13:\"1; mode=block\";s:15:\"x-frame-options\";s:10:\"SAMEORIGIN\";s:22:\"x-content-type-options\";s:7:\"nosniff\";s:25:\"strict-transport-security\";a:2:{i:0;s:44:\"max-age=31536000; includeSubdomains; preload\";i:1;s:16:\"max-age=15768000\";}s:23:\"content-security-policy\";s:26:\"upgrade-insecure-requests;\";s:4:\"vary\";s:23:\"Accept-Encoding, Cookie\";s:7:\"expires\";s:29:\"Thu, 19 Nov 1981 08:52:00 GMT\";s:13:\"cache-control\";s:35:\"no-store, no-cache, must-revalidate\";s:6:\"pragma\";s:8:\"no-cache\";s:4:\"etag\";s:34:\"\"af54c4b554ade61f9f7a26917632edfe\"\";s:12:\"x-robots-tag\";s:15:\"noindex, follow\";s:3:\"via\";s:10:\"1.1 google\";s:7:\"alt-svc\";s:5:\"clear\";s:14:\"x-sucuri-cache\";s:3:\"HIT\";}}s:5:\"build\";s:14:\"20190617084556\";}', 'no');
